reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:160:      "Huangbo, Transmission of Mind, sections on using mind to seek mind and nothing to obtain, https://wayofsuddenawakening.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Huang-Po-The-Transmission-of-Mind.pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:161:      "Dogen Bendowa and shusho itto, Soto Zen explanation with Bendowa quotation, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:164:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit used accessible primary translations, open academic articles, prior Lumenary audits, and practitioner-facing Zen sources. It did not fully review Pargament's original 1988 article, Katz's Language, Epistemology, and Mysticism, Lindbeck, Sharf, Ferrer monographs, Longchenpa in Tibetan, Sanskrit or Pali originals, or actual practitioner interviews. Novelty should not rise without those checks.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:165:    "structural_observation": "The close read supports a broader architecture variable, but not credit distribution alone. Brihadaranyaka 3.7.23 asserts an inner seer and knower through a cosmological inner-ruler grammar; it does not show a reported pressure after practice. SN 22.59 applies an ownership and control test to all aggregates and ends in disenchantment, dispassion, release, and knowledge of release; it does not leave a witness as the text's authorized remainder. Huangbo strains the sequence because it rejects using mind to seek Mind and treats objectified seeking itself as the mistake. Dogen strains it differently: practice and realization are one, so the cause-result and claimant sequence is collapsed rather than managed downstream. These sources suggest that method-reflexivity, search grammar, and practice-realization may be as upstream as credit distribution."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:174:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Pargament, Katz, Lutz, VCE, MPE research, Ferrer, and prior Lumenary remainder and credit models, this idea says the key test is incremental prediction: credit distribution should partly predict when subject-shaped residue appears, while residue should still add predictive information after credit distribution and practice-reflexivity have been coded. Without that incremental result, the idea is only a refined consolidation."
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface.md:56:- Ask Jodo Shinshu and Dzogchen teachers whether register-sensitive interface mapping avoids self-power or psychological distortion, or whether even this second-order mapping remains misleading.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:18:- Different primary texts model different endings: MN 22 releases the raft after right use, Heart Sutra negates attainment while retaining reliance, Mandukya allows a known Self, Rinzai koan work exhausts ordinary thinking while remaining curriculum, and Dogen collapses before and after through practice-realization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:29:Structural observation: MN 22 is a close primary near-neighbor for validated-then-released method. It teaches right grasp, crossing, and release of the raft, so the candidate's set-down category is old. The Heart Sutra complicates the model because it negates attainment yet retains reliance on Prajnaparamita and mantra. This supports the candidate's claim that undermining result does not always mean abandoning method. Mandukya adds a different pressure: negation culminates in the Self that is to be known. Dogen strains the whole after-completion frame because practice and realization are inseparable, so return is not a later test but the practice itself.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:31:Secondary literature gap: The audit found strong near-neighbors in Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Sells on unsaying, Asad, Lindbeck, Sharf, VCE, Hadot-style spiritual exercises, Zen oxherding return motifs, and Buddhist raft or upaya literature. It did not read the full books by Smith, Sells, Hadot, Hori, Lindbeck, Katz, or Sharf, and it did not consult original Sanskrit, Pali, Chinese, Japanese, Greek, Latin, Arabic, or Tibetan.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:41:- "Dogen" "practice and realization are one" Bendowa
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:48:- Dogen Bendowa material, Everyday Zen Foundation, https://everydayzen.org/teachings/dogens-bendowa-part-2-of-3/: overlap: Close anomaly and near-neighbor. Dogen's practice-realization already says practice is not a means to a later result and realization is not an object privately recognized after practice.; difference: The candidate makes Dogen an anomaly inside a return model, whereas Dogen may reject the whole before, peak, after sequence.; novelty impact: Lowers confidence. If Dogen is central rather than marginal, the return test may be only an external heuristic.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:51:- Lindahl, Fisher, Cooper, Rosen, and Britton, VCE, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239: overlap: Close for the safety and aftercare surface. VCE tracks distress, impairment, appraisals, remedies, teacher guidance, and integration after meditation-related experiences.; difference: VCE does not organize completion by result-standing versus result-undermining and retained, released, or embodied method.; novelty impact: Keeps some room for novel synthesis, but only if the rubric predicts aftercare better than VCE's broader influencing-factor domains.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:52:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://bpb-ap-se2.wpmucdn.com/thinkspace.csu.edu.au/dist/c/3891/files/2020/10/Asad-Anthropology.pdf, and George Lindbeck summarized at https://people.bu.edu/wwildman/bce/mwt_themes_862_lindbeck.htm: overlap: Both anticipate the idea that practice, doctrine, grammar, institution, authority, and correct performance shape what counts as proper use and outcome.; difference: They do not provide the exact return grid or the burnout-facing practice prompt.; novelty impact: Downgrades the broad theory. The possible contribution is a narrow testing protocol, not a new account of religious practice.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:56:Unlike the raft simile, apophatic unsaying, therapeutic readings of Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Dogen practice-realization, VCE aftercare, Asad's discursive tradition, and Lindbeck's doctrine grammar, this idea's distinct claim is a practical comparative test: code whether a method validates or undermines the result, then code whether the method is retained, released, or embodied, and see whether that interaction predicts warnings, re-entry duties, identity risks, and repairs better than doctrine, institution, teacher style, or clinical-risk variables alone.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:60:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization, radical Other Power in Tannisho, inherited communal religion, and successful ordinary ethical practice without a marked peak experience.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:62:Why it strains the model: These cases resist the sequence of method, result, and return. Dogen makes practice and realization inseparable. Tannisho relocates efficacy to Amida's Vow and can make nembutsu non-practice from the practitioner's side. Inherited religion may not have a discrete completion event. Ordinary ethical formation may return without peak experience at all.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:76:- Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization and Rinzai koan curriculum
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:116:- Close-read Tannisho, Dogen Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Rinzai koan curriculum source, Cloud of Unknowing or Dionysius, a Dzogchen pointing-out source, and one Sufi fana or baqa source before raising source reliability.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-does-the-remainder-handling-profile-framework-generate-predictions-that-no-single.md:9:The challenger defeated the proponent's original claim that remainder pressure is a pre-interpretive, universal hidden variable across contemplative traditions. The proponent conceded that different negation methods (neti neti, aggregate analysis, Madhyamaka prasanga, Dzogchen pointing-out) are structurally different operations producing different phenomenologies, not different interpretations of one common intermediate state. The Madhyamaka case proved decisive: Nagarjuna and Candrakirti diagnose the search for a remainder as itself a form of grasping, which means the framework cannot treat their tradition as one more management strategy for a pressure it denies exists. The proponent revised the claim to treat remainder pressure as a method-conditioned diagnostic variable rather than an independent one, preserving the distinction between the subject-remainder impulse and the policy each tradition uses to handle it, while acknowledging that the impulse is downstream of entry architecture and practice method. The challenger accepted the revision as genuine but raised a deeper unresolved question: whether the revised framework adds predictive value beyond what each tradition's own corrective literature already provides, or whether it is taxonomy rather than theory.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-does-the-remainder-handling-profile-framework-generate-predictions-that-no-single.md:17:When practitioners switch between contemplative methods with different remainder-handling profiles (e.g., from Vedantic neti neti to Theravada aggregate analysis, or from Dzogchen recognition to Madhyamaka analytical meditation), do interference patterns emerge that neither tradition's corrective literature anticipates? If so, do those patterns track the distance between remainder-handling profiles, and can they be predicted from the entry architecture and negation method of each tradition?
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-whether-the-separability-thesis-survives-the-method-dependency-concession-if-con.md:13:Whether the separability thesis survives the method-dependency concession. If contemplative training shapes not only how practitioners interpret the pressure but whether the pressure arises at all, then occurrence and interpretation are entangled from the start. The clean analytic cut between them may be a useful methodological fiction rather than a phenomenological discovery. Cross-trained practitioners could test the empirical question (does the same person report pressure during Advaita inquiry and not during Dzogchen practice?), but even positive results would show learned repertoire rather than settle whether the pressure has a single phenomenological character across training contexts.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit.md:21:- Claude turn 1 challenge, which made no-boundary, Dogen practice-realization, and Shinran Other Power load-bearing anomalies.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit.md:62:- Test the Dogen and Jodo Shinshu pair to see whether shared authority relocation predicts specific permissions, warnings, safeguards, or re-entry obligations rather than merely sharing a code value.
