reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.json:107:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.57 to 0.39. The structural logic is heavily anticipated by Collingwood, Gadamer, Austin, Asad, Lindbeck, spiritual-bypassing research, VCE, and local Lumenary sentence-role and no-management records. Preserve as an extended test protocol only if the imported-question field predicts failures and repairs beyond those baselines.",
