reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.json:127:      "religion scholars familiar with Asad and Lindbeck",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.json:135:      "Dogen Bendowa excerpts and Soto shusho itto, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf, read against Huangbo, https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a2-chun-chou-record-cont.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.json:138:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Read Collingwood, Gadamer, Austin, Searle, Asad, Lindbeck, Sharf, Katz, Pargament, spiritual bypassing research, VCE, Cheetah House, Pure Land studies on hakarai and Other Power, Dogen scholarship on practice-realization, and koan curriculum scholarship by Hori or Rinzai specialists before raising novelty.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.json:139:    "structural_observation": "SN 22.59 permits a disciplined question sequence: is this aggregate controllable, permanent, easeful, fit to regard as mine, self, or what I am? Shinran answers a doctrinal question by refusing calculation on the practicer and relocating assurance to Other Power. Dogen blocks separation of cultivation and realization, while still warning against clever slogans and requiring practice. Huangbo explicitly challenges the question What is the Way and how must it be followed? The candidate's strongest form is not that questions are bad, but that each source licenses a different question grammar with different failure modes."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.json:151:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Collingwood, Gadamer, Austin, Asad, Lindbeck, spiritual-bypassing research, and prior Lumenary sentence-role records, this idea predicts that the practitioner's imported question itself is a codeable failure variable that can create post-insight distance before any remainder question is asked."
observations/codex/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning.md:54:- Test paired traditions with shared context and different entry grammars: Zen and Jodo Shinshu, Calvinist and Wesleyan Christianity, Dzogchen and gradual-path Gelug.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:95:      "source": "George Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine, cultural-linguistic doctrine-as-grammar, overview example https://www.kci.go.kr/kciportal/ci/sereArticleSearch/ciSereArtiView.kci?sereArticleSearchBean.artiId=ART001871058"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:101:      "source": "Talal Asad, Genealogies of Religion, https://press.jhu.edu/books/title/1644/genealogies-religion"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:116:      "difference": "Dogen's structure is native to transmitted Zen practice, not an open rule for borrowing sentences from other traditions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:119:      "source": "Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.jasonong.com/5499 and secondary discussion of Dogen's realization-based language, https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/12/2/81"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:170:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.50 to 0.46. The doctrine half is close to Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Sandmel, Lindbeck, Asad, and prior Lumenary translation-strain gates. The seeker half is close to Jamesian fruits, Ignatian discernment, Dogen practice-realization, Wuthnow's seeker spirituality, Turkle's conversation critique, social prescribing, behavioral activation, and anti-checking psychology. The contribution is a compact routing rule by function and wound. Human-condition fit is plausible but narrow: stable lonely or digitally unmoored seekers with meaning loss, feeling out of place, digital comparison, or achievement-contingent spiritual identity. Practice-testability drops sharply without a pre-contact safety screen and delayed provenance review.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:173:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Originality falls if practitioners identify the protocol as standard discernment of fruits, spiritual direction, pastoral counseling, teacher guidance, Jamesian fruit testing, Lindbeck-style grammar, Panikkar-style comparison, social prescribing, behavioral activation, or CBT anti-rumination in new terms. It also falls if they cannot distinguish contact-first from ordinary advice to talk to someone before posting.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:198:      "Dogen, Genjokoan, Aitken and Tanahashi translation, https://www.jasonong.com/5499, read against James and Ignatius as a practice-realization pressure case"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:201:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Read pastoral discernment and spiritual-direction literature directly, especially Ignatian discernment manuals, contemporary spiritual direction ethics, Buddhist teacher-student guidance, interfaith pastoral counseling, and religious appropriation ethics. Also read Wuthnow on seeking and practice-oriented spirituality, Roof and Bender on spiritual bricolage and lived spirituality, Pargament on religious coping, Turkle on digital conversation, Salkovskis and Rachman on checking and reassurance, social prescribing evidence, behavioral activation for social connectedness, and prior Lumenary records on translation strain, correction holders, and anti-overchecking.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:202:    "structural_observation": "James already separates origin from value and gives a fruits-over-roots test for religious life. Ignatius operationalizes a practitioner version: movements are discerned by where they lead, by timing, by desolation safeguards, and by disclosure to a competent spiritual person. Dogen adds a different enacted-test structure: realization is not certified before practice, it occurs in doing and returning to the place of practice. These sources strongly anticipate the contact-and-conduct side. The candidate's distinct move is not conduct-testing itself, but routing: source-first for public claim, contact-first for stable private orientation, then delayed provenance before teaching or identity authority."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:211:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Sandmel, Lindbeck, Asad, James, Ignatius, Dogen, Wuthnow, Turkle, social prescribing, anti-checking psychology, and recent Lumenary translation-strain records, this candidate's specific contribution is a two-track routing rule: borrowed language used as public doctrine or evidence must pass provenance and regeneration first, while borrowed language used privately by a stable lonely seeker should first be carried into safe contact and conduct so it does not become a substitute for belonging, repair, grief work, or help-seeking."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:12:Before asking what a practice does with authority over its result, ask whether it claims to produce a separable result at all. Custody, release, and correction vocabulary applies only to instrumental practices. Dogen's practice-realization and Shinran's Other Power dissolve the tool frame because sitting or entrusting is not owned as a means to a later product.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:18:- Dogen's practice-realization makes sitting not a bridge to later enlightenment but the expression of realization itself.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:27:- Dogen shusho itto and Shinran jinen honi, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf and https://shinranworks.com/hymns-in-japanese/hymns-of-the-dharma-ages/on-jinen-honi/
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:29:Structural observation: MN 22 is explicitly instrumental: effort with the raft gets one across, then the raft should not be carried. Dogen's shusho itto demolishes the cause-effect separation between practice and realization, while Shinran's jinen honi removes calculation by the practicer and locates efficacy in Other Power. The contrast supports a scope distinction, but not a discovery: the instrumental versus non-instrumental contrast is already structurally visible in the primary texts.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:33:Risk of overread: High. Non-instrumental self-description does not mean absence of discipline, correction, warnings, institutional form, or effects. Dogen still requires continuous practice, and Shinran still has nembutsu, entrusting, and cautions. The model may confuse no owned result with no practical structure.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:37:- Dogen shusho itto practice realization one cause effect practice realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:45:- Pargament religious problem solving styles agency God control
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:49:- Internal Lumenary audit, When There Is Nothing To Keep Or Release, reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json: overlap: Extremely close. The prior audit already says keep, release, embody assumes practitioner ownership and a discrete after, and that Shinran and Dogen break those assumptions.; difference: This candidate uses the broader word instrumentality and asks whether the practice claims to produce a separable result.; novelty impact: Major internal downgrade. The scope-gate framing is useful but not a new discovery.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:51:- Dogen shusho itto, Soto Zen key term, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: Very close. The source states that shusho itto demolishes the generally accepted cause-effect relation between practice and realization.; difference: The candidate turns this into a scope rule for Lumenary's custody apparatus.; novelty impact: Downgrades the Dogen example to known Soto doctrine.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:55:- Pargament et al., religious problem-solving styles, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for agency distribution between individual and divine action, especially deferring and collaborative styles.; difference: Pargament studies coping and control attribution, not whether a practice produces a separable result.; novelty impact: For Shinran-style agency relocation, novelty is low unless the separable-result gate predicts warnings beyond agency-style variables.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:59:Unlike Dogen's practice-realization, Shinran's Other Power, autotelic activity theory, non-instrumental ritual theory, MacIntyre's internal goods, and prior Lumenary non-ownership audits, this idea's possible contribution is a practical scope gate for comparative coding: ask first whether a practice claims to produce a separable result before applying custody, release, or correction vocabulary.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:71:- If: The separable-result question is a real scope gate. Then: Texts and manuals coded as non-instrumental from doctrinal passages will show less result-custody language and more conduct, form, vow, teacher, or community correction language in held-out sources. Weakens if: Self-described non-instrumental traditions contain result-custody language as centrally as instrumental traditions, or coders cannot distinguish result refusal from result relocation. Test surface: Split-source coding of Dogen, Shinran, MN 22, koan curricula, Advaita inquiry, apophatic Christian sources, Sufi fana and baqa, and ritual manuals.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:78:- Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:113:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.34. The instrumental versus non-instrumental distinction is old and appears directly in Dogen, Shinran, ritual theory, autotelic activity theory, and prior Lumenary non-ownership audits. The useful extension is narrower: using separable-result as a pre-coding scope gate for Lumenary's custody and release apparatus. Human-condition fit is strong for functioning perfectionists, founders, students, creators, and professionals who convert every activity into proof of worth. It is not for under-motivation, responsibility avoidance, severe depression, dissociation, mania, psychosis, addiction withdrawal, acute crisis, coercive workloads, or people who need concrete completed outcomes restored before resultless practice is safe.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:120:- Read non-instrumental ritual theory, autotelic flow literature, MacIntyre on practices, Dogen's Eihei Shingi, Bendowa and Genjokoan, Shinran and Tannisho in stronger translations before public use.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you-426c0c34cd74415c.md:31:Secondary literature gap: Before publication, read Ignatian spiritual-direction ethics, VCE and Cheetah House materials, OCD and scrupulosity reassurance-seeking literature, ACT defusion and committed action, rumination stop-rule research, behavioral activation, achievement-contingent self-worth, perfectionism, spiritual bypassing, and spiritual-abuse literature. The largest empirical gap is whether no-verdict plus ordinary care beats classification-first, rest, conversation, and clinician-guided routing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you-426c0c34cd74415c.md:33:Risk of overread: Very high if generalized. Advaita, Dzogchen, Mahamudra, clear-light sleep, and direct-recognition lineages may treat some quiet or objectless reports as trainable evidence within strict contexts. In OCD, scrupulosity, trauma, dissociation, mania, severe depression, and unsafe authority settings, the instruction can become avoidance, checking, reassurance outsourcing, or control.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you-426c0c34cd74415c.md:39:- Lindahl Britton Varieties of Contemplative Experience meditation challenges interpretation support remedies
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you-426c0c34cd74415c.md:48:- Lindahl et al., Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE 2017, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239: overlap: Close on separating phenomenology from interpretation, causes, remedies, teacher relationships, social context, distress, impairment, and needed support.; difference: VCE is descriptive and broader. It does not prescribe a twenty-four-hour no-verdict return to ordinary care.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. The candidate may be a practice-facing distillation of VCE-style support routing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you-426c0c34cd74415c.md:78:- Advaita, Dzogchen, Mahamudra, and sleep-yoga teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you-426c0c34cd74415c.md:120:- Add a direct-recognition anomaly set before public use: Advaita, Dzogchen, Mahamudra, clear-light sleep, and competent teacher-held recognition.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life.md:21:- Practitioner-method source: Dogen's practice-realization in Bendowa, via local prior work and Bielefeldt's Dogen's Manuals of Zen Meditation, used as a lens for testing truth through enacted practice. Critique of the lens: it can make source history look secondary even when community, lineage, and harm require source accountability.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life.md:85:Survived critique from comparison theory, the Chandogya and SN 22.59 carrier conflict, Dogen's practice-realization pressure, social-connection grounding, and checking-risk cautions by narrowing the claim into two distinct gates.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life.md:158:- Result: Preliminary search found strong overlap with Smith, Freiberger, Panikkar, Wuthnow, Dogen scholarship, and OCD checking literature. Novelty should stay moderate and depend on the two-gate operational distinction.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life.md:160:- Next action: Read Asad, Lindbeck, Katz, Sharf, Wuthnow, and spiritual-bypassing literature before raising novelty.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:25:- Dogen Bendowa excerpts and Soto shusho itto, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf, read against Huangbo, https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a2-chun-chou-record-cont.htm
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:27:Structural observation: SN 22.59 permits a disciplined question sequence: is this aggregate controllable, permanent, easeful, fit to regard as mine, self, or what I am? Shinran answers a doctrinal question by refusing calculation on the practicer and relocating assurance to Other Power. Dogen blocks separation of cultivation and realization, while still warning against clever slogans and requiring practice. Huangbo explicitly challenges the question What is the Way and how must it be followed? The candidate's strongest form is not that questions are bad, but that each source licenses a different question grammar with different failure modes.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:29:Secondary literature gap: Read Collingwood, Gadamer, Austin, Searle, Asad, Lindbeck, Sharf, Katz, Pargament, spiritual bypassing research, VCE, Cheetah House, Pure Land studies on hakarai and Other Power, Dogen scholarship on practice-realization, and koan curriculum scholarship by Hori or Rinzai specialists before raising novelty.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:38:- Lindbeck doctrine grammar religion practice training rules
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:39:- Asad discursive tradition correct form purpose practice authority
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:40:- wrong question spiritual bypassing meditation self improvement burnout
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:48:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://voidnetwork.gr/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Idea-of-an-Anthropology-of-Islam-by-Talal-Asad.pdf: overlap: Asad already treats tradition as discourse instructing practitioners about correct form and purpose, with authority and correction internal to practice.; difference: The candidate narrows correct form and purpose to the practitioner's initiating question after self-negation.; novelty impact: Strong downgrade for the tradition-held permission claim.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:49:- George Lindbeck cultural-linguistic doctrine-as-grammar summaries, https://people.bu.edu/wwildman/bce/mwt_themes_862_lindbeck.htm and https://scielo.org.za/scielo.php?pid=S2074-77052018000100007&script=sci_arttext: overlap: Lindbeck already makes doctrine a rule or grammar regulating religious speech and practice.; difference: The candidate predicts a specific modern failure when a self-owned completion question violates that grammar.; novelty impact: Moderate downgrade; retain only as empirical-practice extension.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:54:Unlike Collingwood, Gadamer, Austin, Asad, Lindbeck, spiritual-bypassing research, and prior Lumenary sentence-role records, this idea predicts that the practitioner's imported question itself is a codeable failure variable that can create post-insight distance before any remainder question is asked.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:66:- If: The imported-question variable is real and separable from prior models. Then: Blind coders can identify a source's permitted, refused, or transformed question before reading outcome passages, and those labels predict held-out warnings or repairs better than sentence-role, support-holder, tradition label, or VCE-factor baselines alone. Weakens if: Coders need outcome passages to infer the question, cannot agree, or the variable adds no predictive power beyond existing source-role and correction-holder rubrics. Test surface: A/B inter-rater coding on SN 22.59, SN 22.95, Shinran letters, Tannisho, Bendowa, Huangbo, Dzogchen direct introduction, and Rinzai koan materials.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:77:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:80:- religion scholars familiar with Asad and Lindbeck
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-question-can-make-the-distance-30eeb13d9da3a2bc.md:111:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.57 to 0.39. The structural logic is heavily anticipated by Collingwood, Gadamer, Austin, Asad, Lindbeck, spiritual-bypassing research, VCE, and local Lumenary sentence-role and no-management records. Preserve as an extended test protocol only if the imported-question field predicts failures and repairs beyond those baselines.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:28:- Huangbo, Transmission of Mind, sections on using mind to seek mind and nothing to obtain, https://wayofsuddenawakening.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Huang-Po-The-Transmission-of-Mind.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:29:- Dogen Bendowa and shusho itto, Soto Zen explanation with Bendowa quotation, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:31:Structural observation: The close read supports a broader architecture variable, but not credit distribution alone. Brihadaranyaka 3.7.23 asserts an inner seer and knower through a cosmological inner-ruler grammar; it does not show a reported pressure after practice. SN 22.59 applies an ownership and control test to all aggregates and ends in disenchantment, dispassion, release, and knowledge of release; it does not leave a witness as the text's authorized remainder. Huangbo strains the sequence because it rejects using mind to seek Mind and treats objectified seeking itself as the mistake. Dogen strains it differently: practice and realization are one, so the cause-result and claimant sequence is collapsed rather than managed downstream. These sources suggest that method-reflexivity, search grammar, and practice-realization may be as upstream as credit distribution.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:33:Secondary literature gap: This audit used accessible primary translations, open academic articles, prior Lumenary audits, and practitioner-facing Zen sources. It did not fully review Pargament's original 1988 article, Katz's Language, Epistemology, and Mysticism, Lindbeck, Sharf, Ferrer monographs, Longchenpa in Tibetan, Sanskrit or Pali originals, or actual practitioner interviews. Novelty should not rise without those checks.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:39:- Pargament religious problem solving styles self directing deferring collaborative agency attribution
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:43:- Varieties of Contemplative Experience framework influencing factors meditation adverse effects Lindahl Britton
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:47:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization one shusho itto
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:54:- Pargament et al. religious problem-solving and coping styles, self-directing, deferring, collaborative, summary and scale discussion at https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC1630686/ and https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for assigning responsibility between person, God, or both, and for predicting different psychological correlates from agency orientation.; difference: Pargament studies coping and control, not cross-tradition self-negation residue or contemplative remainder reports.; novelty impact: High reduction for the upstream agency variable. The candidate must beat this baseline.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:57:- Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE 2017, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239: overlap: Very close for separating phenomenology, interpretation, causal attribution, management strategy, teacher influence, demand characteristics, and practitioner or practice-level factors.; difference: VCE is broader and safety-oriented; it does not propose credit distribution plus remainder pressure as a specific two-variable model.; novelty impact: High reduction for the empirical protocol and anti-priming caution.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:63:Unlike Pargament, Katz, Lutz, VCE, MPE research, Ferrer, and prior Lumenary remainder and credit models, this idea says the key test is incremental prediction: credit distribution should partly predict when subject-shaped residue appears, while residue should still add predictive information after credit distribution and practice-reflexivity have been coded. Without that incremental result, the idea is only a refined consolidation.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:67:Candidate: Huangbo search-refusal, Dogen practice-realization, and Dzogchen direct recognition cases where the tradition rejects the search sequence rather than producing a downstream remainder to manage.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:69:Why it strains the model: These cases do not cleanly fit a two-stage order of upstream credit distribution followed by downstream pressure. Huangbo says the search for Mind by mind is the problem, Dogen collapses practice and realization, and Dzogchen-style recognition can treat effortful attainment as an obscuration. If these cases are central rather than marginal, the upstream variable is not credit distribution but search grammar or reflexivity policy.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:71:Confidence effect: Lowers originality and confidence. The model remains useful as a synthesis, but should be downgraded from candidate discovery to extended unless it predicts cases that Reflexivity Policy, Pargament, Lutz, and VCE do not.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:77:- If: Safeguard profiles should reflect the interaction between architecture and residue. Then: Manuals and teachers should warn against pride where practitioner credit and residue reification combine, passivity where source credit dominates, gaining idea where activity-centered practice is misunderstood, and premature realization where ground-centered or recognition architectures meet strong residue. Weakens if: Warning clusters are better predicted by institution, authority structure, trauma history, retreat dosage, teacher style, or generic spiritual bypassing than by the architecture-residue interaction. Test surface: Blind coding of warnings and repairs in manuals, teacher interviews, and VCE-style adverse-event cases.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:87:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with pointing-out instruction
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:88:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:91:- Psychologists of religion familiar with Pargament and religious attribution
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:94:- Is this model more than Pargament agency styles plus Katz contextualism plus Lutz or VCE practice-factor coding?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:100:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners say the model is ordinary agency, grace, self-power and other-power, spiritual bypassing, nondual warning, or lineage pedagogy in new language. They cannot identify predictions that differ from Pargament, VCE, Lutz, Reflexivity Policy, or existing teacher warnings.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:120:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.78 to about 0.52. The synthesis is useful and testable, but both halves are already present in prior Lumenary audits, and the exact upstream-downstream move is closely anticipated by Claude's Reflexivity Policy. External prior art also strongly anticipates the core structure: Pargament for agency distribution, Katz for tradition-shaped experience, Lutz for multidimensional practice coding, VCE for interpretation and management of contemplative effects, MPE and nondual-awareness research for residue-like phenomenology, and Ferrer for participatory co-creation. The remaining contribution is a separability and incremental-prediction protocol.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.md:128:- Compare predictive power against Pargament agency styles, Katz contextualism, Lutz Phenomenological Matrix, VCE influencing factors, MPE and nondual-awareness questionnaires, Ferrer participatory theory, spiritual bypassing and spiritual materialism literature, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:28:- Dogen shusho itto source from Soto Zen, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:30:Structural observation: Orange is a near-exact high-severity case: prayer, will, desire, assent, and the beginning of faith are attributed to grace, not unaided nature. Tannisho supplies a vow-held analogue, where entrusting to Amida's Primal Vow displaces self-power and reshapes warning language. SN 22.59 does not fit the same entry grammar, because it negates ownership of aggregates and moves through disenchantment and release without clearly requiring an external break mechanism. Dogen is the strongest anomaly: practice and realization are treated as one, and beginner practice is already implicated in realization, so entry and fruition cannot be cleanly sequenced as threshold and later attainment.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:32:Secondary literature gap: The audit checked accessible primary translations, local prior Lumenary audits, and open sources on conversion, liminality, doctrine-as-grammar, religious coping, legitimate peripheral participation, contemplative adverse effects, grace, Other Power, and practice-realization. It did not fully review Rambo's full monograph, Lindbeck's full book, Japanese, Pali, Sanskrit, Tibetan, Latin, or Chinese originals, Shinran scholarship, Dogen scholarship, Sufi bayah and fana sources, Dzogchen pointing-out manuals, or practitioner interviews.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:42:- "doctrine as grammar" Lindbeck cultural linguistic religion
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:43:- "religion problem solving process" Pargament self-directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:48:- "Dogen" Bendowa practice realization shusho itto
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:56:- George Lindbeck, doctrine as grammar and cultural-linguistic religion, https://people.bu.edu/wwildman/bce/mwt_themes_862_lindbeck.htm and https://www.saet.ac.uk/Christianity/TheologicalLanguage: overlap: Very close for treating doctrine as a rule-like grammar that shapes religious speech, practice, identity, and coherent participation.; difference: Lindbeck does not isolate beginning grammar into incapacity, threshold, break mechanism, and residue policy, nor require held-out prediction of warnings and repairs.; novelty impact: High reduction for the grammar frame. Novelty depends on operational prediction.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:57:- Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for distributing agency between person and God through self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles, and for predicting different outcomes from that distribution.; difference: Pargament studies coping and problem-solving, not entry into transformative practice after self-negation or vow-held and grace-held beginning.; novelty impact: High reduction for support-locus and agency-distribution claims.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:62:- Dogen practice-realization and shusho itto, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: Strong anomaly and near-neighbor for no-threshold entry: practice and realization are one, and beginner practice is already original realization.; difference: The candidate can code this only by adding no-threshold, no-break, practice-realization, and analyst-frame-refused values.; novelty impact: High anomaly pressure. Without these values the model overreaches.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:63:- Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239: overlap: Close for factor-separated contemplative outcomes, including practitioner factors, practice factors, relationships, health behaviors, interpretation, and management of difficult experiences.; difference: VCE does not propose entry grammar plus residue authorization as a textual predictor of safeguards and repairs.; novelty impact: High methodological reduction. Any empirical test must beat VCE-style factor coding.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:68:Unlike Rambo, Lofland-Stark, Van Gennep, Turner, Lindbeck, Pargament, Lave and Wenger, Orange, Shinran, Dogen, VCE, Meno-style inquiry paradoxes, and prior Lumenary entry-residue records, this idea says entry should be coded through four interacting fields, incapacity, minimum participation, break mechanism, and residue policy, and that first-break type becomes irreducible only where a tradition denies that ordinary self-generated threshold entry can found the path.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:72:Candidate: Inherited religious formation and Dogen-style practice-realization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:74:Why it strains the model: In inherited formation, there may be no discrete threshold act, no single first break, and no separate residue policy available to the beginner. In Dogen-style practice-realization, beginning and realization are not cleanly separated, so the entry grammar may be the same as the fruition grammar. These cases force the model to include no-threshold, no-break, continuous-authorization, practice-realization, and analyst-frame-refused values.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:80:- If: High-severity traditions that deny self-generated threshold entry should show distinctive warnings against self-credit or self-powered attainment. Then: Entry texts coded as grace-held, vow-held, or teacher-recognition entry should predict held-out warning texts targeting pride, self-effort absolutism, unauthorized claim-making, despair, passivity, or premature certainty. Weakens if: If held-out manuals from these traditions warn no more against self-credit than matched traditions with ordinary participation thresholds, the first-break variable loses predictive force. Test surface: Split-source coding across Orange and Augustinian grace texts, Tannisho and Shinran letters, Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, and matched Theravada or Confucian cultivation texts.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:82:- If: Residue policy should interact with entry grammar rather than merely duplicate it. Then: Two traditions with similar entry thresholds but different residue policies should show different verification rules and different forbidden claimant warnings. Weakens if: If residue policy adds no predictive gain beyond entry mechanism, support locus, social ecology, and tradition identity, the compound model should collapse into simpler entry or agency models. Test surface: Compare Theravada no-self analysis, Advaita self-inquiry, Pure Land Other Power, Soto practice-realization, and Dzogchen recognition using inter-rater coding and held-out warning manuals.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:83:- If: First-break should be non-universal. Then: Gradual cultivation, inherited practice, legitimate peripheral participation, and practice-realization cases should be codeable without a first-break field, or should receive a no-break or analyst-frame-refused value. Weakens if: If all cases require first-break accounting, the conditional claim is false. If none do after controls, the first-break field is unnecessary. Test surface: Initial six-case trial: Theravada sangha entry, Confucian cultivation, Jodo Shinshu, Augustinian grace, Zen great doubt, and Dzogchen pointing-out.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:92:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:125:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.54. The four-field compression is useful, but most components have strong near-neighbors in prior Lumenary audits, conversion theory, rites-of-passage theory, doctrine-as-grammar, religious problem-solving styles, legitimate peripheral participation, grace theology, Pure Land Other Power, Dogen practice-realization, VCE factor coding, and Meno-style inquiry paradoxes. The remaining contribution is a conditional first-break rule plus a split-source predictive test, not a discovery-level doctrine candidate.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:134:- Compare predictive value against Rambo conversion stages, Lofland-Stark conversion conditions, Van Gennep and Turner liminality, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, Pargament agency styles, Lave and Wenger legitimate peripheral participation, upaya pedagogy, religious socialization, VCE factor coding, transformative learning theory, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:135:- Test six initial cases: Theravada sangha entry, Confucian cultivation, Jodo Shinshu, Augustinian grace, Zen great doubt, and Dzogchen pointing-out.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:19:- Mode chosen: Critique. Active frontier: remainder pressure after self-negation, especially anomalies from Dogen practice-realization, radical Other Power, inherited communal practice, and search-refusal cases.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:20:- Primary-text comparison: SN 22.59 Anattalakkhana Sutta treats form, feeling, perception, formations, and consciousness as not fit for ownership; Dogen's Uji treats practice-enlightenment and the present act as already time-being; Shinran's Kyogyoshinsho places true entrusting and nembutsu under Other Power rather than self-power.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:21:- Practitioner-method lens: early Buddhist de-identification from SN 22.59 was used to ask what cannot be owned; Dao De Jing chapter 48 non-forcing and Dogen's Uji were used to correct the method so negation does not erase lived support.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:22:- Closest prior-art pressure: Clark and Chalmers, The Extended Mind; Joel Krueger, Extended Mind and Religious Cognition; Talal Asad on discursive tradition; George Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar. These already show external, communal, textual, and institutional supports shaping religious cognition and practice.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:27:The model may still smuggle a support story into traditions that reject support-seeking. Huangbo's search-refusal, Dogen's practice-realization, and early Buddhist not-self may not be variants of prior support; they may be instructions to stop reifying practice time, ownership, and attainment. Shinran's Other Power can also become a theological claim that should not be translated into a general human lesson. The modern practice may harm people whose real need is agency, safety, boundaries, or clinical support. This should remain under dialogue until lineage readers and practitioner reports confirm that already-carried support changes diagnosis rather than redescribes ordinary belonging.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:81:Critique mode pressure from Dogen practice-realization, Shinran Other Power, Huangbo search-refusal, SN 22.59 not-self, extended religious mind prior art, discursive-tradition prior art, and modern loneliness and perfectionism sources.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:167:- Next action: Build a small corpus from SN 22.59, Dogen, Shinran, Huangbo, Advaita self-inquiry, Pure Land, Dzogchen pointing-out, and Christian grace texts; pre-register coding rules before scoring.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you.md:193:- Close-read Dogen's Bendowa and Uji, Shinran's Kyogyoshinsho and Tannisho, Huangbo's Transmission of Mind, and SN 22.59 for timing verbs: begin, receive, practice, realize, seek, entrust, abandon, enact.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Dogen practice-realization and inherited religious participation.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "Dogen-style practice-realization collapses the ordinary sequence of beginning, method, and fruit. Inherited participation may have no salient first-break event. Both cases strain a model that assumes transformation begins through a narratable threshold and later authorizes a remainder."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:33:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Warnings are predicted equally well by generic tradition identity, teacher style, Pargament agency style, Rambo conversion stage, VCE factors, or social ecology, with no incremental gain from the interaction term."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:38:      "test_surface": "Paired comparison of Advaita self-inquiry, Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out, Zen encounter, and Christian spiritual direction.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:44:      "test_surface": "Within-family and cross-family comparisons: Pure Land, Christian grace, Soto Zen, Dzogchen, and Advaita.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:65:    "\"doctrine as grammar\" Lindbeck cultural linguistic religion",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:66:    "\"religion problem solving process\" Pargament self-directing deferring collaborative",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:69:    "\"Dogen\" Bendowa practice realization shusho itto",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:72:    "\"Varieties of Contemplative Experience\" worldview teacher practice factors"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:94:      "difference": "Lindbeck does not build an entry-residue coding sheet with held-out predictions for warnings and repairs.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:97:      "source": "George Lindbeck, doctrine as grammar and cultural-linguistic theory, summarized at https://people.bu.edu/wwildman/bce/mwt_themes_862_lindbeck.htm and https://www.commonwealmagazine.org/church-postliberal-age"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:100:      "difference": "Pargament studies religious coping, not entry into transformative practice after self-negation, nor source-layer coding of residue.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:103:      "source": "Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:112:      "difference": "The candidate can include this as no-threshold or practice-realization, but Dogen is not easily treated as entry plus later residue.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:115:      "source": "Dogen practice-realization and shusho itto, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:127:      "source": "Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:142:    "Compare predictive power against Rambo conversion stages, Lofland-Stark conversion conditions, Van Gennep and Turner liminality, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, Pargament agency styles, Lave and Wenger situated learning, upaya, religious socialization, VCE factor coding, and prior Lumenary ledgers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:147:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.53. The synthesis is useful and testable, but most components have strong near-neighbors: conversion theory for entry process, rites-of-passage theory for thresholds, Lindbeck for grammar, Pargament for agency distribution, Shinran and Orange for vow or grace-held beginnings, Dogen for practice-realization collapse, VCE for factor-separated contemplative outcomes, and prior Lumenary audits for residue, first-break, entry-state, threshold grammar, claimability, support, and operational remainder ecology. The remaining contribution is a split-source interaction test with additive predictive burden.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:164:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:176:      "Dogen Bendowa and shusho itto, Soto Zen source, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:180:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit checked accessible primary translations, local prior Lumenary audits, and open sources on conversion, rites of passage, doctrine-as-grammar, religious coping, situated learning, Pure Land Other Power, Christian grace, and practice-realization. It did not fully review Rambo's full monograph, Lindbeck's full book, Japanese, Pali, Sanskrit, Tibetan, Latin, or Chinese originals, Shinran scholarship, Dogen scholarship, Sufi bayah and fana sources, Dzogchen pointing-out manuals, or practitioner interviews.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:181:    "structural_observation": "The primary texts support an interaction field but also reduce originality. Tannisho makes entry depend on entrusting to Amida's vow, relocates decisive efficacy to Other Power, and warns against self-power, teacher ownership, and self-will. SN 22.59 negates ownership of the five aggregates and moves through disenchantment, release, and knowledge of release, without authorizing a hidden self as remainder. Dogen strains the sequence because practice and realization are one, so beginning and fruit cannot be cleanly separated. The Gita complicates the model by mixing action, multiple causes, divine inner rulership, and final surrender, so one text may contain several entry-residue logics by chapter and voice."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:190:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Rambo, Van Gennep, Turner, Lindbeck, Pargament, Lave and Wenger, VCE, Shinran, Dogen, Orange, and prior Lumenary ledgers, this idea says the key test is additive prediction: independently coded residue authorization and entry grammar should interact to predict held-out safeguards, warnings, effort theories, verification rules, and repairs better than entry-only, residue-only, agency-style, social-ecology, tradition-identity, or source-layer baselines."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:57:    "comparative method religion provenance translation strain Smith Freiberger Panikkar Lindbeck Asad",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:58:    "spiritual bypassing borrowed spiritual language avoidance unresolved grief responsibility",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:100:      "difference": "Dogen is not giving a general rule for cross-tradition borrowing by eclectic seekers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:103:      "source": "Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.thezensite.com/ZenTeachings/Dogen_Teachings/GenjoKoan_Aitken.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:109:      "source": "Talal Asad, Genealogies of Religion, publisher page https://press.jhu.edu/books/title/1644/genealogies-religion, and George Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar overview example https://www.kci.go.kr/kciportal/ci/sereArticleSearch/ciSereArtiView.kci?sereArticleSearchBean.artiId=ART001871058"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:133:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.44 to 0.32. The local prior Contact Before Claim already contains the same two-track routing rule. External prior art strongly covers disciplined comparison, fruits-testing, discernment, action-before-identity, traditioned grammar, social connection, spiritual bypassing, and anti-checking. Keep only as a safety-focused restatement unless blind distinct-content testing shows separability.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:161:      "William James, The Varieties of Religious Experience, https://www.gutenberg.org/files/621/621-h/621-h.html, read against Ignatius of Loyola, Spiritual Exercises discernment rules, https://www.ignatianspirituality.com/making-good-decisions/discernment-of-spirits/rules-for-discernment/ and Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.thezensite.com/ZenTeachings/Dogen_Teachings/GenjoKoan_Aitken.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:164:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Before any publication, read spiritual-direction ethics, pastoral counseling, Buddhist teacher-student guidance, comparative theology, Bucar on religious appropriation, Wuthnow on seeking versus practice-oriented spirituality, Turkle on mediated conversation, Pargament on religious coping, spiritual bypassing literature, social prescribing evidence, and OCD checking and reassurance research directly. The candidate is too close to prior Lumenary records to stand without a blind distinct-content test.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:165:    "structural_observation": "Chandogya authorizes identity with subtle essence and Atman, while SN 22.59 refuses ownership and self-identification for all aggregates, including consciousness. That supports a strict doctrine gate. James already shifts religious judgment toward fruits, Ignatian discernment tests movements by effects, timing, desolation safeguards, and disclosure to a competent spiritual person, and Dogen resists certifying realization apart from enacted practice. These primary sources strongly anticipate contact, conduct, and correction as tests of lived use."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:177:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Smith, Freiberger, Panikkar, James, Ignatius, Dogen, Lindbeck, Asad, Wuthnow, Turkle, spiritual-bypassing literature, social prescribing, OCD reassurance research, and recent Lumenary contact-before-claim records, this candidate's only distinct claim is that a valid doctrine-protection test should not be handed to a lonely person as medicine unless it demonstrably increases safe contact, conduct, correction, and belonging."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Bahiya's immediate release, Tannisho's non-practice Other Power, and Dogen's practice-realization collapse the model's tendency to locate direction in analyzable layers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "Bahiya receives a brief instruction and is said to be released immediately, so textual coding cannot show whether direction came from prior training, readiness, teacher authority, or the instruction itself. Tannisho denies self-owned practice calculation and assigns decisive efficacy to Other Power, so calling nembutsu a directed practice can distort the source. Dogen-style practice-realization refuses a clean sequence of practice first and result later, so layer location may be an analyst imposition."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:28:      "expected_observation": "Layer scores should predict held-out warnings and repairs above baselines using tradition name, technique family, teacher style, social ecology, Pargament agency style, Lutz matrix dimensions, and VCE factors.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:30:      "test_surface": "Six-case corpus: MN 10, Vivekachudamani, Tannisho, Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, and The Cloud of Unknowing.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:59:    "George Lindbeck Nature of Doctrine cultural linguistic rule theory doctrine grammar",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:61:    "Pargament religious problem-solving styles self-directing deferring collaborative",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:62:    "Lindahl Britton Varieties of Contemplative Experience influencing factors practice practitioner relationships health behaviors",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:86:      "difference": "Lindbeck is mainly theological and doctrinal, not a micro-phenomenological or adverse-practice transfer model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:88:      "overlap": "Close structural prior. Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic and rule-theory model treats doctrine as grammar internalized through practice and training, shaping religious experience and judgment.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:89:      "source": "George Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine, Open Library record, https://openlibrary.org/works/OL5607588W/The_nature_of_doctrine"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:113:      "source": "Lindahl, Fisher, Cooper, Rosen, and Britton, Varieties of Contemplative Experience, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:116:      "difference": "Pargament studies religious coping and problem-solving, not fine-grained contemplative instruction layers or cross-tradition transfer.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:119:      "source": "Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:140:    "Compare predictive value against Dunne mindfulness styles, Lutz phenomenological matrix, Lindbeck grammar, Pargament agency styles, habitus and hysteresis, situated learning, VCE factors, teacher style, social ecology, intensity, and clinical-risk baselines.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:143:    "Use Bahiya, Tannisho, Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, direct introduction, and successful dual practice as anomaly classes rather than confirming examples.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:146:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.78 to about 0.42. The useful contribution is not the broad claim that practices carry direction through many layers. That is strongly anticipated by primary texts, Dunne, Lutz, Lindbeck, Foucault, Hadot, Bourdieu, Pargament, VCE, situated learning, Sharf, Katz, and prior Lumenary ledgers. The surviving extension is the pre-registered split-source test: code where direction enters, then predict warnings, repairs, transfer resistance, and adverse effects.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:162:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:179:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model can become too absorbent if every difference is assigned to some layer after the fact. Tannisho and radical Other Power traditions can reject the analyst's practice-direction frame. Dogen-style practice-realization can collapse means and result. Bahiya-style immediacy strains any developmental layer sequence. Community, doctrine, teacher style, clinical risk, and social belonging may explain many cases without this model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:180:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The search found strong near-neighbors in Dunne on Buddhist mindfulness styles, Lutz, Jha, Dunne, and Saron on the phenomenological matrix, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Foucault on technologies of the self, Hadot on spiritual exercises, Bourdieu and Wacquant on habitus and hysteresis, Pargament on religious problem-solving styles, Lave and Wenger on situated learning, Sharf and Katz on context-shaped experience, and Lindahl and Britton's VCE study. This audit did not read full monographs by Lindbeck, Asad, Hadot, Bourdieu, Katz, or Sharf, did not check Pali, Sanskrit, Tibetan, Japanese, Middle English, or Chinese terms, and did not include practitioner interviews.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:190:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Dunne, Lutz, Lindbeck, Foucault, Hadot, Bourdieu, Pargament, VCE, Sharf, Katz, and prior Lumenary ledgers, the surviving distinct claim is a split-source predictive rule: code where practice direction enters before reading outcomes, then test whether layer mismatch predicts warnings, repairs, transfer resistance, and adverse effects better than technique, tradition label, social ecology, teacher style, and clinical risk. The general idea that practice has layered direction is not original."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "No-threshold entry: inherited practice and Dogen's practice-realization grammar, especially Bendowa's claim that beginner practice is already original realization and that there is no beginning in practice.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:56:    "Pargament religion problem solving process three styles coping self directing deferring collaborative",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:62:    "Dogen Bendowa practice realization beginner practice realization translation",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:75:      "novelty_impact": "High reduction for agency-locus claims. Moderate remaining novelty if the ledger predicts entry safeguards beyond Pargament's styles.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:76:      "overlap": "Close for responsibility distribution. Pargament already distinguishes self-directing, deferring, and collaborative religious problem-solving styles by how agency is assigned between person and God.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:77:      "source": "Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:107:      "source": "George Lindbeck, cultural-linguistic theory of religion and doctrine as grammar, summarized in Boston Collaborative Encyclopedia of Western Theology, https://people.bu.edu/wwildman/bce/mwt_themes_862_lindbeck.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:134:    "Use inherited-practice and Dogen-style no-beginning cases as anomaly tests rather than marginal examples.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:136:    "Do not raise above novel_synthesis unless split-source blind coding predicts safeguards or failure modes better than conversion studies, Pargament agency styles, upaya, liminality, situated-learning, and religious-socialization variables."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:138:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.64. The distributed-entry and threshold pieces are strongly anticipated by Rambo's conversion model, liminality, situated learning, religious socialization, upaya, Pargament's agency styles, Engler's prerequisites, Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic grammar, and Shinran's Other Power. The remaining contribution is a promising operational synthesis: a split-source predictive rubric linking entry capacity loci to tradition-specific warning and repair patterns.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:155:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with pointing-out",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:167:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit searched conversion theory, religious coping, legitimate peripheral participation, liminality, upaya, transformative learning, religious socialization, Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic model, Shinran, SN 45.8, Dogen, Augustine, and the Council of Orange. It did not sufficiently close-read Kyogyoshinsho beyond the Chapter on Practice, Augustine and Pelagius in full primary-text sequence, Longchenpa or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, Sufi bayah and fana texts, or original-language terms for entrusting, effort, vow, grace, and capacity. That gap blocks a candidate-discovery claim.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:177:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike conversion-process theory, religious coping theory, upaya pedagogy, situated learning, liminality theory, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar model, Engler's capacity prerequisites, and Shinran's Other Power grammar, this idea claims that path entry can be coded as a pre-practice distributed ledger plus a normative beginning grammar, and that this pairing should predict later safeguards, warnings, verification practices, and failure modes better than either entry ecology or doctrine alone."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "If a vipassana-trained practitioner can move into Advaita self-inquiry, devotional surrender, or Dzogchen recognition without attention persistently tracking impermanence, non-ownership, or analytic deconstruction, then grain may be a comparative description rather than a lived capacity structure. Chan, Zen, modern cross-training, and eclectic contemplative therapy are especially important anomaly classes."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:11:    "The same named capacity, such as attention or self-observation, functions differently in Theravada, Advaita, Sufism, Pure Land, Dzogchen, and Soto Zen.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:35:      "expected_observation": "Vivekachudamani-style qualifications should define readiness in terms of the real versus unreal and longing for liberation. Satipatthana and later insight manuals should define readiness through impermanence, suffering, non-ownership, and ethical abandonment. Sufi manuals should orient self-knowledge toward creaturely dependence before God. Dzogchen manuals should orient preparation toward devotion, introduction, recognition, and non-distraction.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:54:    "Lindahl Britton varieties contemplative experience adverse meditation interpretation practice context",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:92:      "source": "Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:106:    "Run a small practitioner test with at least one teacher each from Theravada, Advaita, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Sufism, and Pure Land, asking whether grain changes practice sequencing."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:123:      "Dzogchen and Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.json:135:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Search found strong near-neighbors in Katz's constructivism, Sharf on meditative experience and bare attention, Dunne on Buddhist styles of mindfulness, Ferrer's participatory theory, Hadot-style spiritual exercises, Engler's developmental prerequisite thesis, Lindahl and Britton's VCE work, and local Lumenary work on attentional instruments and verification architecture. I did not find the exact phrase grain of capacity or a specific claim that prerequisites, rather than experiences, are directionally carved toward the dissolution they enable. Still, most structural components are known.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:26:- Dogen Bendowa practice-realization, read through Carl Bielefeldt, Dogen's Manuals of Zen Meditation, https://www.ucpress.edu/books/dogens-manuals-of-zen-meditation/pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:28:Structural observation: Chandogya 6.8.7 authorizes identity through the repeated Self teaching, while SN 22.59 dismantles ownership of the aggregates, including consciousness, through impermanence and lack of control. The same surface function, loosening ordinary identity, is carried by incompatible verification rules. Dogen adds pressure against treating a sentence apart from enacted practice. This supports a carrier-context warning, but it does not prove that contact-first routing is original.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Read Freiberger on comparison, Jonathan Z. Smith on comparison, Panikkar on homeomorphic equivalence, Ammerman and McGuire on lived religion, Mercadante and Bender on SBNR struggle, Pargament on religious coping, Welwood and spiritual-bypassing scholarship, cultural appropriation work on yoga and mindfulness, and OCD reassurance-checking literature before treating this as more than a routing synthesis.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:39:- Pargament religious coping meaning control comfort intimacy transformation RCOPE
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:41:- spiritual bypassing John Welwood spiritual ideas avoid emotional wounds
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:50:- Pargament religious coping model and RCOPE, example overview https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/1/1/28 and methods paper https://www.kennethpargament.com/_files/ugd/fb472f_b39305e5a153454c903d1b87a27e3475.pdf: overlap: Pargament already codes religious coping by function, including meaning, control, comfort, intimacy with others, transformation, and maladaptive forms.; difference: The candidate applies function testing to borrowed cross-tradition sentences and separates private coping from public doctrine.; novelty impact: Significant downgrade for the seeker-fruit test. The novelty is only the comparative-religion routing frame.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:59:Unlike Freiberger, Smith, Panikkar, lived religion, Pargament, spiritual-bypassing work, appropriation studies, reassurance-checking research, and prior Lumenary routing records, this idea's narrow contribution is a two-gate rule: provenance first for public doctrine, contact and correction first for stable lonely seekers using a borrowed sentence privately.
