reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.json:104:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.57 to 0.28. The core is already present in the supplied Who Holds The Gate audit and has close external neighbors in Ignatian direction, spiritual direction, Pargament agency styles, contemplative adverse-effects support, ERP anti-reassurance rules, and self-focused-attention research. Human-condition fit is real but bounded: it serves stable high-achievement practitioners, founders, students, creators, caregivers, and self-directed meditators who convert insight into worth evidence. It is not for acute crisis, mania, psychosis, severe depression, dissociation, addiction withdrawal, active OCD or scrupulosity reassurance loops, abusive authority settings, or people whose main need is restored self-trust.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.json:130:      "MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, Heart Sutra, Shinran On Jinen-Honi, and Dogen Bendowa or practice-realization sources, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html, https://www.lotsawahouse.org/words-of-the-buddha/heart-sutra, https://shinranworks.com/letters/lamp-for-the-latter-ages/on-jinen-honi-1258/, https://buddhismnow.com/2023/10/08/practice-within-realisation-dogen/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.json:132:    "risk_of_overread": "High. External holding can be wise guidance, ordinary sponsorship, clinical triage, coercive authority, approval dependence, or OCD reassurance. No-check can mean healthy rest, avoidance, depression drift, or Dogen-style non-instrumentality. The bypasser, scorer, and oscillator labels are too crude without validated measures and concrete behavior markers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.json:133:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Still needs full reading of Ignatian directorial manuals, contemporary spiritual direction ethics, AA sponsorship sources, ERP and scrupulosity treatment literature, VCE person-centered support, spiritual bypassing literature, and achievement-contingent self-worth studies before practice publication.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.json:134:    "structural_observation": "Ignatius is the closest primary-text neighbor. The director adapts exercises to the exercitant, receives reports of movements and thoughts, reveals dangerous secrecy to a confessor or spiritual person, and is also restrained from seizing the exercitant's final choice. The scruple notes already distinguish useful sensitivity from harmful over-fineness and counsel a mean. MN 22 adds that the raft must be grasped correctly before release, so release is not a generic self-check. The Heart Sutra denies attainment while retaining reliance on Prajnaparamita. Shinran and Dogen strain the whole model because no-calculation and practice-realization refuse a clean separable product that the practitioner can audit."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.json:146:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Ignatian direction, Pargament agency styles, VCE support mapping, ERP anti-reassurance rules, and the prior Lumenary Who Holds The Gate record, this candidate says that a post-practice check must first ask who should hold the diagnostic today, because the same check can repair bypassing and worsen achievement-contingent self-scoring. That distinction is useful, but it is mostly a renamed and narrower safety-routing heuristic."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Read Proudfoot on religious experience attribution, Sharf on experience and Buddhist modernism, Katz and Taves on interpretation, Asad and Lindbeck on tradition and grammar, Alston on doxastic practice and defeaters, VCE literature on appraisal and support, spiritual direction ethics, abuse literature, and clinical material on meditation-related adverse effects.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:41:- Talal Asad discursive tradition correct form purpose practice orthodoxy power
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:43:- Lindahl Britton Varieties Contemplative Experience appraisal support social context meditation challenges
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:52:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://voidnetwork.gr/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Idea-of-an-Anthropology-of-Islam-by-Talal-Asad.pdf; George Lindbeck, cultural-linguistic doctrine summaries such as https://people.bu.edu/wwildman/bce/mwt_themes_862_lindbeck.htm: overlap: Close on tradition as instruction in correct practice, authority, grammar, and regulated correction.; difference: The candidate frames correction as epistemic safety for a post-gap report, not as a full theory of tradition.; novelty impact: Moderate to strong reduction.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:54:- Lindahl, Britton, Cooper, and Kirmayer, Challenging and Adverse Meditation Experiences, Oxford Handbook chapter, https://bpb-us-w2.wpmucdn.com/sites.brown.edu/dist/f/330/files/2023/10/Lindahl-2019-Oxford-Handbook-of-Meditation-chapter.pdf; Cheetah House FAQ, https://www.cheetahhouse.org/faq: overlap: Close on appraisal, social context, support needs, and the danger of mislabeling meditation-related challenges.; difference: The candidate uses these concerns as epistemic criteria for post-gap claims.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction, with strong safety support.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:58:Unlike Ignatian discernment, Jamesian fruits, Proudfoot, Sharf, Asad, Lindbeck, Alston, VCE safety work, and prior Lumenary correction-holder records, this idea says that post-self-questioning silence should not count as usable evidence unless a named accepted corrector can overrule the returned interpretation. The narrowing is useful, but the structure is mostly renamed prior art.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:72:- If: Traditions that claim direct recognition still retain some corrective channel. Then: Advaita, Dzogchen, Zen, and apophatic sources that speak of direct recognition still point to conduct, teacher verification, scripture, vows, lineage, compassion, or ordinary functioning as later constraints. Weakens if: Mature sources explicitly authorize private recognition with no teacher, text, conduct, or communal check, and practitioners show stable integration without such checks. Test surface: Close reading plus practitioner interviews asking for concrete misrecognition and repair cases.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:80:- Advaita and Dzogchen teachers who teach direct recognition
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:90:- Can you describe a case where correction itself caused shame, dependence, abuse, or spiritual bypassing?
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.md:113:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.56 to 0.24. The claim is a clear, useful restatement of prior Lumenary correction-holder work and close external near-neighbors in Ignatian discernment, James, Proudfoot, Sharf, Asad, Lindbeck, Alston, and VCE safety literature. Human-condition fit is strong but narrow: isolated stable practitioners facing loneliness, meaning loss, and unsupported interpretation after unusual quiet. It is not for acute crisis, psychosis, mania, paranoia, dissociation, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, fresh grief, abusive communities, or cases needing medical or clinical care.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-practice-load-and-scaffold-fit.md:24:- Primary and near-neighbor sources cited in the dialogue: SN 22.59, Chandogya Upanishad 6.8.7-6.16, Shinran's Tannisho and Kyogyoshinsho, Engler on being somebody before being nobody, Lindahl et al. on meditation-related challenges.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "If even hearing, saying, entrusting, and gratitude are Amida's working rather than trained human functions, then the analyst's transfer language may smuggle self-power into a tradition built to reject that framing. Dogen also strains the model because practice-realization collapses bridge and arrival rather than transferring ownership from one holder to another."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:27:      "expected_observation": "Pure Land texts should warn against calculation, Dzogchen texts against contrivance and premature recognition, Soto texts against gaining idea, early Buddhist texts against appropriation of aggregates or attainment ownership, and Gita-style karma-yoga texts against fruit ownership.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:40:      "if_model_is_right": "The handoff rubric should add predictive value beyond Pargament-style responsibility allocation and the local capacity ledger.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:41:      "test_surface": "Inter-rater coding of matched pairs such as Soto and Dzogchen, Pure Land and Christian grace, Theravada and karma-yoga.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:54:    "Pargament self-directing deferring collaborative religious coping styles problem solving responsibility God",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:58:    "Dogen practice-realization not means to end shusho",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:68:      "source": "Pargament et al., religious problem-solving styles, summarized at https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC1630686/ and https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:89:      "difference": "Dogen is one type within the proposed rubric, not the whole comparative model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:92:      "source": "Dogen practice-realization, St Andrews Encyclopaedia of Theology, https://www.saet.ac.uk/Buddhism/Dogen and Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy, https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/japanese-zen/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:116:    "Code primary manuals before broad tradition labels, beginning with SN 45.8, Tannisho chapters 1, 6, 8, and 11, Longchen Rabjam Trekcho, Bendowa or Dogen practice-realization sources, and one Christian grace manual.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:121:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.53 to about 0.44. The rubric is generative, but its parts are heavily anticipated by religious coping styles, self-power and other-power discourse, Dogen, Dzogchen manuals, the raft and upaya pattern, Engler, and local Lumenary priors. Treat as a consolidation unless inter-rater coding shows new predictive value.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:134:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:148:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The search found close prior structures in religious coping styles, self-power and other-power, Dogen practice-realization, Dzogchen direct introduction, Engler on ego strength before no-self, the Buddhist raft and upaya pattern, and local Lumenary capacity-ledger and credit-distribution work. I did not find the exact field list as a cross-tradition coding sheet, but the core agency-allocation and means-end reversal are well established.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.json:161:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Pargament, self-power and other-power debates, Dogen practice-realization, and local Lumenary credit models, this idea says the decisive unit is a timed transfer for each required function, with observable safeguards and repairs at that transfer point."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "If a text or practice intentionally collapses the distinction between denial, refusal, and recognition, the authorization-mode grid may impose categories the source rejects. Dogen practice-realization, Dzogchen pointing-out, Mahamudra direct introduction, and some Madhyamaka sources may make authorization inseparable from performance and relation, not a codeable stance after an event."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:31:      "test_surface": "Split-source coding study across Brihadaranyaka, Shankara, SN 22.59, SN 22.95, Udana 1.10, MMK 18.6, Dogen, Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, and contemporary mindfulness adverse-event guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:58:    "George Lindbeck doctrine as grammar religious language practice interpretation",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:59:    "Talal Asad discursive tradition authorized practice anthropology religion",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:63:    "Varieties of Contemplative Experience interpretation support meditation adverse effects identity distress"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:85:      "difference": "Lindbeck is not focused on post-negation contemplative states, and does not supply the candidate's stratum-specific post-state safety test.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:88:      "source": "George A. Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine, doctrine-as-grammar model"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:91:      "difference": "Asad is an anthropology of tradition, not a post-negation contemplative codebook. The candidate adds objectless-state and de-identification scope.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:94:      "source": "Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, discursive tradition, https://web.stanford.edu/class/educ356/Readings/Asad_The_Idea_of_an_Anthropology_of_Islam.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:112:      "source": "Lindahl et al., Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE 2017, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:122:    "Compare predictive value against Katz contextualism, Sharf, Lindbeck, Asad, Madhyamaka scholarship, Advaita svaprakasha studies, VCE, Cheetah House materials, Pargament agency styles, and prior Lumenary correction-holder models.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:143:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:155:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Before raising novelty, compare directly with Steven Katz on contextualist mystical experience, Robert Sharf on experience as rhetorically and institutionally authorized, George Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Talal Asad on discursive tradition, Madhyamaka non-positioning, Advaita work on svaprakasha and adhyasa, and contemplative-science papers that separate levels of explanation in neuroscience translation. Also compare with internal Lumenary records: Residual Burden of Proof After Negation, The Inferential Gap, The Brain Model Already Took a Side, and You Cannot Prove the One Who Is Asking.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.json:165:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Katz, Sharf, Lindbeck, Asad, Madhyamaka non-positioning, Advaita self-luminosity debates, VCE support routing, and prior Lumenary inference-policy records, this candidate says post-negation counsel and comparison should be coded by the same three controls: authorization mode, source stratum, and observed practitioner effect. That is a useful synthesis and protocol refinement, not a standalone discovery yet."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "The idea assumes that private review is often the burden for depleted over-managers. If structure and review are the relieving container, then the model confuses over-management with the absence of safe holding. It also fails if Other Power, Dogen practice-realization, or community-held practice includes rigorous review, conduct correction, and formal repetition without harming agency."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:31:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Coders cleanly apply keep, release, and embody axes across Shinran, Dogen, Heart Sutra, MN 22, and apophatic sources without distortion, and the three fit variables do not predict held-out warnings or repairs."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:55:    "Pargament religion problem-solving process three styles of coping self-directing deferring collaborative",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:59:    "Dogen practice realization no gaining Bendowa Genjokoan",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:72:      "difference": "Pargament is broader coping theory, not a practice-ending fit gate for contemplative methods after they help.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:75:      "source": "Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, 1988, indexed at https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:121:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.36 to 0.31. The contribution is a useful scoped fit gate, but it heavily overlaps prior Lumenary holder-routing records, Pargament agency styles, ACT, rumination and self-focused attention research, Buddhist non-grasping, apophatic unsaying, and meditation-safety routing. Publishability should remain modest until the model shows predictive gain over ordinary discernment, spiritual direction, ACT, and clinical triage. Human-condition fit is clear but narrow: burned-out over-managers, compulsive self-monitors, and people with achievement-contingent self-worth. It is not for under-reflectors, acute grief, crisis, severe depression, dissociation, mania, addiction withdrawal, abusive authority contexts, or cases needing accountability and material help.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:147:      "Dogen practice-realization sources such as Bendowa or Genjokoan; Shinran and Tannisho Other Power sources, including https://shinranworks.com/commentaries/notes-on-once-calling-and-many-calling/ and Tannisho chapter 8 translations."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:150:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit still needs direct term-level work on Shinran's jinen honi and hakarai, Dogen's shusho-itto or practice-realization, apophatic unsaying, spiritual direction ethics, and ACT or CBT literature on self-monitoring. Source reliability is adequate for lowering novelty, not for promoting the model as a discovery.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:151:    "structural_observation": "MN 22 supports a tool-use and non-clinging pattern: a teaching can be used for crossing and then not possessed. The Heart Sutra strains a simple release rule because it denies attainment while preserving reliance on prajnaparamita. Dogen-style practice-realization strains it further because practice is not merely an instrument awaiting later review. Shinran Other Power also resists practitioner-owned handling because merit and final efficacy are not primarily self-managed. The candidate's strongest move is not method-release, which is old, but the fit gate that asks whether ownership, temporality, and available agency exist before prescribing review."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:163:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Pargament's agency styles, ACT's critique of internal control, Buddhist non-grasping, apophatic unsaying, Cheetah House safety routing, and prior Lumenary correction-holder records, this idea says that after-use review itself should be blocked unless three fit conditions are present: provisional ownership, a permitted after, and spare agency. That is useful, but mostly an extension of known parts."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:30:      "test_surface": "Split-source blind coding across Soto Zen, Rinzai Zen, Jodo Shinshu, Theravada, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Christian spiritual direction, Sufism, and secular mindfulness.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:31:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Held-out predictions are no better than broad tradition identity, teacher style, institutional policy, or generic Asad-Lindbeck authority coding."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:34:      "expected_observation": "Pairs such as Dogen practice-realization and Shinran Other Power can share only a narrowly stated structure, such as refusal of self-owned attainment, while still predicting different warnings and permissions. Confirmed matches should be rare, specific, and tied to held-out observations.",
