reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:79:      "source": "Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://voidnetwork.gr/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Idea-of-an-Anthropology-of-Islam-by-Talal-Asad.pdf; George Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine; Max Weber, sociology of religious authority."
