reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:158:      "Dogen Bendowa practice-realization sources, for example https://everydayzen.org/teachings/dogens-bendowa-part-2-of-3/, read against Shinran and Jodo Shinshu Other Power sources, for example https://www.nembutsu.info/standard/nature_faith.htm",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:162:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Before promotion, read Asad on discursive tradition, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Weber on religious authority, Bell on ritualization, Sharf and Katz on experience and context, Freiberger and J. Z. Smith on comparison, Popper and Mayo on test structure, Lachs on Zen authorization, Ann Gleig and Amy Langenberg on Buddhist misconduct and survivor-centered method, IICSA and FaithTrust safeguarding materials, AIFS on spiritual and religious abuse, VCE and Cheetah House on meditation-related difficulties, plus actual ethics codes from Soto Zen, Insight, Vajrayana, Christian spiritual direction, and interfaith settings.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:163:    "structural_observation": "Dogen strains the boundary model because practice and realization are not cleanly separable, so a category such as continuous practice-realization must not be treated as just another boundary type. Shinran strains the same model from another side: efficacy is relocated to Amida's vow and Other Power, not to a practitioner-owned method or generic support system. These two cases may both refuse self-owned attainment, but their warnings differ: Dogen pressure falls on expecting realization outside practice, while Shinshu pressure falls on self-power calculation. Lachs then shows that Zen authorization language and transmission mechanisms can legitimate hierarchy and authority while creating problems in Western Zen. The safety sources add a further split: religious authority, community trust, and doctrinal legitimacy can coexist with coercion, silence, institutional betrayal, or inadequate survivor response."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.json:172:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Asad, Lindbeck, Weber, Freiberger, Smith, Popper, Lachs, Gleig and Langenberg, VCE, Cheetah House, safeguarding literature, and the parent Lumenary records, the only separable contribution is a combined protocol: code native authority ecology from one source layer, pre-register match grain and held-out predictions before any positive convergence verdict, then report native legitimacy and safety adequacy as separate outputs for human use. The broader ideas are not new."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:26:- Dogen Bendowa and Soto practice-realization sources, https://www.lionsroar.com/just-wholeheartedly-sit/ and https://www.sotozen.com/eng/library/stories/vol01.html, read against Shinran's Kyogyoshinsho, https://shinranworks.com/the-major-expositions/chapter-on-practice/
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:28:Structural observation: SN 22.59 removes ownership from the aggregates, but SN 45.2 already makes admirable friendship central to path cultivation, which makes no one begins alone textually old. Dogen's Bendowa does not simply say support came before the self; it says practice and realization are not two separable items, while still preserving master, transmission, trust, and authentic teacher. Shinran places practice and shinjin under Amida's Vow and Other Power, so translating this into generic prior support risks turning a theological grammar into a self-help support inventory. The support-timing labels are operationally useful, but the claim is mostly a recoding of existing support, grace, transmission, and community structures.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Before any public claim, read internal Lumenary records No One Begins Alone and What Holds You That You Did Not Build; Clark and Chalmers on extended mind, https://consc.net/papers/extended.html; Joel Krueger on extended religious cognition, https://philarchive.org/rec/KRUTEM-2; Pargament on religious problem-solving styles; Talal Asad on discursive tradition; Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar; secure-base and social baseline theory; AA Twelve Steps, https://www.aa.org/the-twelve-steps; Dogen scholarship on shusho-itto; Shinran scholarship on hakarai and Other Power; Huangbo and Chan no-seeking sources; and loneliness, burnout, and perfectionism sources.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:38:- Clark Chalmers "The Extended Mind" reliable external resources
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:39:- Joel Krueger "Extended Mind and Religious Cognition" ritual sacred space
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:40:- Pargament religion problem solving self directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:42:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization one authentic teacher trust
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:50:- Clark and Chalmers, The Extended Mind, https://consc.net/papers/extended.html, and Joel Krueger, Extended Mind and Religious Cognition, https://philarchive.org/rec/KRUTEM-2: overlap: Close. External artifacts, bodies, language, culture, rituals, sacred spaces, songs, and other people can partly constitute cognition or religious cognition rather than merely assist it.; difference: The candidate applies distributed support to self-emptying practice and to achievement-contingent self-sufficiency.; novelty impact: Strong downgrade for the support ontology. Possible extension remains only in the support-timing failure test.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:51:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, indexed at https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Very close on support and agency location. Self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles already code whether problem-solving is carried by the self, God, or a shared relation.; difference: This candidate broadens holders beyond God to teacher, vow, ritual, community, present act, body, and practical supports, then asks about timing before self-owned beginning.; novelty impact: Strong downgrade. The timing labels must predict more than agency-style variables to matter.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:53:- Dogen Bendowa and Soto practice-realization sources, https://www.lionsroar.com/just-wholeheartedly-sit/ and https://www.sotozen.com/eng/library/stories/vol01.html: overlap: Close and also anomalous. Practice-realization rejects a simple sequence where practice first builds support and result comes later.; difference: The candidate treats enacted present act as one support-timing category, but Dogen may refuse the entire support-before-support-after frame.; novelty impact: Useful as an anomaly and guardrail, not as confirmation of the model.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:60:Unlike No One Begins Alone, What Holds You That You Did Not Build, extended mind, religious cognition, Pargament, secure-base theory, AA, Dogen, and Shinran, this idea's only separable contribution is a support-timing codebook: code whether support is built, revealed, received, or enacted before reading warnings, then test whether timing predicts failure modes such as pride in surrender, passivity, isolation, or converting help into achievement better than support-locus and social-support baselines.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:64:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization, Huangbo or Chan no-seeking, Shinran radical Other Power, valid solitude, and unsafe community or authority.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:66:Why it strains the model: Dogen and Huangbo may reject the before-after and support-inventory frame because practice is not a tool that leads to a separable result. Shinran may reject the practicer's calculation as self-power. Valid solitude shows that not every beginning requires visible social support, while unsafe community shows that support can be the danger rather than the cure.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:72:- If: Support timing has independent predictive value. Then: Coders who see only entry or instruction passages can classify support as built, revealed, received, or enacted with acceptable inter-rater reliability, then predict held-out warning and repair language better than simpler variables such as social support quality, institution type, teacher contact, or religious coping style. Weakens if: Low coder agreement, or no predictive gain beyond support quality, agency-style, teacher authority, social ecology, and clinical risk. Test surface: Split-source corpus test using SN 22.59, SN 45.2, Dogen Bendowa or Uji, Shinran Kyogyoshinsho and Tannisho, Huangbo, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Christian grace, and one secular mindfulness corpus.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:81:- Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars
