reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:84:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:94:- Does the phrase what was holding me before I tried to be the holder distort Dogen practice-realization, Shinran Other Power, or no-seeking traditions?
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-road-starts-before-you-87cf0ca4a4406eef.md:127:- Close-read SN 45.2, SN 22.59, Dogen Bendowa or Uji, Shinran Kyogyoshinsho and Tannisho, Huangbo, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra source, and one Christian grace source before public wording.
