reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.json:150:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The strongest prior art is Pargament's self-directing, deferring, and collaborative religious coping; Christian monergism and synergism; Japanese Buddhist jiriki and tariki; Sri Vaishnava markata and marjara; Sufi maqam and hal; and religious-attribution or God-control psychology. The searched literature did not show the exact five-type typology with activity-centered and ground-centered categories plus failure-mode predictions, but the main agency-allocation variable is well established.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.json:163:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Pargament, monergism and synergism, self-power and other-power, and markata and marjara debates, this idea adds activity-centered and ground-centered patterns, treats credit attribution as a felt practice variable, and predicts matching failure modes and safeguards across multiple traditions."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:31:Secondary literature gap: The audit searched conversion studies, doctrine-as-grammar theory, religious coping agency styles, sociology of plausibility structures, liminality, situated learning, upaya, Shinran Other Power, Orange grace canons, Dogen practice-realization, religious socialization, and prior Lumenary capacity-ledger audits. It did not fully close-read Augustine against Pelagius, Longchenpa or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, Sufi bayah and fana texts, Sri Vaishnava prapatti sources, or original-language terms for faith, entrusting, effort, capacity, grace, and agency. That gap blocks a candidate-discovery claim.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:33:Risk of overread: High. The phrase grammar risks renaming Lindbeck, Rambo, Pargament, Berger, religious socialization theory, and Lumenary's own Entry-State Ledger unless the candidate produces non-circular coding fields and predictive wins. It also risks imposing analyst-owned agency language on traditions that explicitly refuse the claimant frame.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:39:- George Lindbeck doctrine as grammar cultural linguistic model religion
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:40:- Pargament religion problem solving three styles self directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:43:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization are one translation
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:51:- George Lindbeck, doctrine-as-grammar and cultural-linguistic theory, summarized in Haejong Je, A Critical Evaluation of George Lindbeck's Cultural-Linguistic Theory of Religion, https://www.kci.go.kr/kciportal/ci/sereArticleSearch/ciSereArtiView.kci?sereArticleSearchBean.artiId=ART001871058: overlap: Very close for treating doctrine as a rule-governed grammar that shapes religious language, identity, and practice rather than only expressing propositions or experiences.; difference: The candidate narrows grammar to beginning, agency ownership, support locus, safeguards, and verification across transformative paths.; novelty impact: High reduction for the grammar frame. The possible extension is an operational entry-specific coding instrument.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:52:- Kenneth Pargament et al. religious problem-solving styles, summarized in Watson and Chen, Religious Problem Solving Styles within an American Religious Ideological Surround, https://hc.edu/gideon/wp-content/uploads/sites/79/2023/02/Religious-Problem-Solving-Styles-within-an-American-Religious-Ideological-Surround.pdf: overlap: Close for distributing agency between person and God through self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles.; difference: The candidate applies agency distribution to entry into transformative paths and includes teacher, community, ritual, vow, text, lineage, family formation, and verification rules, not only coping with problems.; novelty impact: High reduction for agency distribution. Moderate extension if the rubric predicts entry failure and repair beyond coping styles.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:59:- Soto Zen teaching on practice and realization, https://www.sotozen.com/eng/library/stories/vol01.html: overlap: Close for practice-realization, where practice is not merely a beginner's method leading later to realization but is already implicated in realization.; difference: The candidate's first-break and claimant categories may not map cleanly onto Dogen-style practice-realization because beginning and fulfillment are deliberately collapsed.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction and strong anomaly pressure. Dogen-style cases may force values such as no-transfer, practice-realization, or analyst-frame-refused.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:65:Unlike Rambo's conversion-process model, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar model, Pargament's religious agency styles, Berger's plausibility structures, upaya pedagogy, liminality theory, Shinran's Other Power grammar, Orange grace theology, religious socialization theory, and Lumenary's Entry-State Ledger, this idea claims that entry mechanism and forbidden claimant form one testable agency grammar, and that a split-source independence audit can determine whether that grammar predicts safeguards and verification practices without circularly reusing the same text as both cause and evidence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:69:Candidate: Inherited practice and Dogen-style practice-realization cases, especially cradle religious formation and Soto Zen's refusal to separate practice from realization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:77:- If: Entry doctrine and claimant prohibition are separable variables in at least some traditions. Then: Blind coders using only entry texts can distinguish entry mechanism from forbidden claimant, and those separate codes predict different warning and verification patterns in later manuals with above-chance agreement. Weakens if: Coders cannot separate entry mechanism from claimant rule, or later safeguards can be predicted equally well from generic tradition labels, conversion-stage theory, religious socialization, or Pargament agency styles. Test surface: Split-source manual coding across Shinran Pure Land, Theravada path-factor texts, Orange or Augustinian grace texts, Dogen practice-realization, and Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:88:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen's practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:89:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with pointing-out instruction
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:121:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.72 to about 0.58. The idea is not a discovery-level concept. Its entry ecology is strongly anticipated by Rambo, Berger, liminality, situated learning, and religious socialization. Its grammar language is anticipated by Lindbeck. Its agency distribution is anticipated by Pargament and grace or Other Power sources. Its support-locus and safeguard rubric is very close to prior Lumenary Entry-State Ledger, Capacity Ledger, Forbidden Claimant, and Credit Distribution records. The remaining contribution is an extension: an independence audit that tries to prevent construct leakage between entry doctrine, claimant rule, anthropology, safeguard, and verification.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:129:- Run a comparison against baseline models: Rambo conversion stages, Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, upaya capacity pedagogy, liminality, situated learning, religious socialization, and prior Lumenary capacity ledger.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.md:130:- Use Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, and successful cross-training as anomaly tests, not as supporting examples.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:12:The keep, release, embody model silently assumes that the practitioner provisionally owns the method and that there is an after in which custody of the result can be decided. Radical Other Power and practice-realization break those assumptions: in Shinran's jinen honi the practitioner never owns the method, trust, or result, while in Dogen's shusho-itto there is no discrete after outside practice. Therefore the custody model is bounded, and for depleted over-managing people the prompt to decide what to keep, release, or embody can become one more burden.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:19:- Dogen's practice-realization refuses the separation between method, verification, and later custody.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:27:- Dogen, Bendowa and shusho-itto practice-realization sources, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:29:Structural observation: Shinran relocates efficacy to Other Power and warns against calculation, so the practitioner is not the owner who later decides how to carry the method. Dogen's practice-realization collapses the gap between practice and verification, so a later custody decision is not the native shape of the path. These are strong boundary cases against a universal after-use grid, but they do not eliminate all guidance: Shin still has nembutsu, warnings, and entrusting language, and Soto still has zazen, discipline, teacher correction, and conduct.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:31:Secondary literature gap: This audit did not read Japanese sources, Dogen commentarial scholarship, Jodo Shinshu scholarship, grace-effort theology, Pargament's full agency-style work, or ethnographic practitioner accounts. It also did not verify whether other traditions with inherited practice, ritual-first formation, or apophatic unsaying similarly refuse the ownership-and-after assumptions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:39:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization one shusho itto verification outside practice
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:40:- Dogen practice and realization are one scholarship
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:42:- Pargament deferring religious coping style agency God control
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:52:- Pargament et al., religious problem-solving styles: overlap: Close for agency relocation away from the individual self and toward divine action, especially deferring and collaborative modes.; difference: Pargament studies coping style and control attribution, not method-completion temporality or practitioner ownership as scope conditions.; novelty impact: Reduces novelty of the agency claim. The candidate must show predictive gain beyond deferring, collaborative, and self-directing agency models.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:57:Unlike Shinran's Other Power, Dogen's practice-realization, Pargament's agency styles, burnout rumination literature, and prior Lumenary release and custody models, this idea's possible contribution is an explicit scope test: before applying keep, release, or embody guidance, first ask whether the tradition grants provisional practitioner ownership and a discrete after, and whether the person has enough agency to benefit from a custody prompt.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:69:- If: Ownership and after are true scope conditions for after-use models. Then: Blind coders can identify texts that grant practitioner ownership and discrete completion separately from texts that relocate or refuse those assumptions, and those codes predict held-out warning and repair patterns. Weakens if: Coders cannot separate refusal from relocation, or retain, release, embody categories work equally well across Shinran, Dogen, Advaita, Theravada, Rinzai, apophatic Christian, and Sufi sources. Test surface: Split-source corpus coding with entry passages, doctrinal passages, and held-out manuals or practitioner interviews.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:77:- Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:110:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.28. The non-ownership and no-after structures are well established in Shinran and Dogen, and the core Lumenary comparison is already present in the recent audit of You cannot release what you never held. The modern caution overlaps with known rumination, perfectionism, and burnout risks. Human-condition fit is strong for depleted over-managers, caregivers, founders, professionals, students, and serious practitioners who turn even rest into performance. It is not for people who need planning, accountability, medication, therapy, social support, or material workload reduction, nor for acute crisis, addiction withdrawal, severe depression, dissociation, psychosis, mania, or responsibility avoidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:117:- Close-read Shinran's Japanese terms around jinen honi and hakarai, Dogen on shusho-itto and non-gaining, and practitioner manuals where concrete guidance appears.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-grid-stays-backstage-c0163823ff1f73cb.md:25:- Dogen, Bendowa excerpts, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf, read against Shinran's reply to Senshin, https://shinranworks.com/letters/a-collection-of-letters-zensho-text/what-we-call-other-power/
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-grid-stays-backstage-c0163823ff1f73cb.md:28:Structural observation: MN 22 supports after-use discipline: a method can be held for crossing and not carried afterward as a burden. Ignatian Examen supports structured review as a legitimate practice, but it frames review as prayer, discernment, gratitude, and concrete amendment rather than private worth-scoring. Dogen strains the tool-result assumption by making cultivation and realization inseparable and warning against clever slogans, while Shinran strains practitioner-owned audit by rejecting calculation in Other Power. The candidate's strongest contribution is not the idea that practices need guidance, or that checking can harm. Those are old. The possible addition is delivery location: the same diagnostic grid may belong backstage as a care-holder's lens, while the practitioner receives only a minimal re-entry act.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-grid-stays-backstage-c0163823ff1f73cb.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Before publication, read full sources in CBT case formulation, ACT, behavioral activation, rumination-focused CBT, MBCT, metacognitive therapy, mood-as-input stop-rule research, ERP and scrupulosity, spiritual direction ethics, Ignatian discernment, upaya pedagogy, Dogen practice-realization scholarship, Pure Land hakarai and Other Power scholarship, VCE, Cheetah House, measurement-based care, and self-monitoring reactivity.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-grid-stays-backstage-c0163823ff1f73cb.md:44:- Dogen practice realization no gaining Bendowa shusho itto
