reviews/originality/2026-05-30-two-channels-of-cross-tradition-likeness-independent-recurrence-and-portability-c0c64ef27ecc1d58.md:32:Secondary literature gap: The audit found strong near-neighbors but still needs full-text work before a high source score: Oliver Freiberger on comparative method, https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/9/2/38 and https://academic.oup.com/book/11633; J. Z. Smith and comparison debates; Asad on discursive tradition; Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar; Katz and Sharf on contextualism; Francis Clooney on comparative theology, https://bpb-ap-se2.wpmucdn.com/thinkspace.csu.edu.au/dist/c/3891/files/2020/10/Clooney-on-Method.pdf; translation studies on domestication, foreignization, and cultural translation; reception history; diffusion and syncretism studies; and historical linguistics on borrowing versus independent innovation.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-two-channels-of-cross-tradition-likeness-independent-recurrence-and-portability-c0c64ef27ecc1d58.md:47:- Varieties of Contemplative Experience support appraisal intervention criteria
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-two-channels-of-cross-tradition-likeness-independent-recurrence-and-portability-c0c64ef27ecc1d58.md:58:- Varieties of Contemplative Experience and Progress or Pathology, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239 and https://www.frontiersin.org/journals/psychology/articles/10.3389/fpsyg.2020.01905/full: overlap: Close on the practical end. These sources already treat context, appraisal, support, impairment, and intervention criteria as necessary for practice safety.; difference: The candidate makes provenance and reception history part of predicting warning and repair profiles for borrowed teachings.; novelty impact: Practice-testability is plausible, but novelty falls unless the provenance-portability split predicts more than existing contextual safety variables.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-two-channels-of-cross-tradition-likeness-independent-recurrence-and-portability-c0c64ef27ecc1d58.md:131:- Compare predictive value against Freiberger-style comparative method, ordinary source criticism, reception history, cultural translation, comparative theology, Lindbeck, Asad, Katz, Sharf, diffusion theory, historical linguistics borrowing controls, VCE safety variables, and prior Lumenary provenance gates.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:31:Secondary literature gap: This audit used accessible primary translations and open academic sources, but did not fully reread Collins, Siderits, Harvey, Albahari, Wilber, Engler's full chapter context, Shinran's Kyogyoshinsho, Dogen scholarship, Dzogchen and Mahamudra manuals, or Britton's full adverse-effects corpus. Pali, Sanskrit, Japanese, and Burmese terms were not checked directly. Stronger novelty would require split-source coding and practitioner interviews.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:38:- meditation adverse effects influencing factors teacher community intensity screening Britton Lindahl
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:39:- Varieties of Contemplative Experience influencing factors practice practitioner relationship health worldview remedies
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:41:- religious coping self-directing deferring collaborative Pargament agency styles
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:42:- doctrine as grammar Lindbeck religion rules practice discourse attitude action
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:43:- Asad discursive tradition religious practice authority discipline
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:53:- Lindahl, Fisher, Cooper, Rosen, and Britton, The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239: overlap: Very close for the training ecology side. VCE studies meditation-related challenges through practice factors, practitioner factors, relationships, health behaviors, teachers, communities, worldviews, appraisals, and remedies.; difference: VCE is a descriptive and clinical taxonomy, not a cross-tradition model linking operational capacities and residue policy after negation to predicted safeguards.; novelty impact: Large reduction. The ecology and adverse-effect claims are already strongly anticipated.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:54:- Lindahl, Palitsky, Cooper, and Britton, The roles and impacts of worldviews in meditation-related challenges, https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/36476189/: overlap: Close for the residue-policy component. The paper treats worldviews as risk factors, remedies, and meaning-making frames that shape the trajectory of meditation-related challenges.; difference: It does not formalize residue policy after self-negation or combine worldview with operational capacity coding.; novelty impact: Moderate to large reduction. Residue policy may be a narrower name for worldview and doctrinal interpretation unless it predicts more.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:57:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for distributing agency and control across self, deity, collaboration, deferral, and surrender, with practical consequences for coping.; difference: Pargament is not focused on contemplative negation or verification after self-dissolution.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. The support-locus and gift-effort categories need baseline comparison against religious coping styles.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:58:- George Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar discussions, https://www.repository.cam.ac.uk/items/351e3c35-6838-49bc-9b33-3ae66dd1fea5: overlap: Close for treating doctrine as rules that regulate religious speech, attitude, action, and communal formation rather than as isolated propositions.; difference: The candidate narrows grammar into residue policy and asks whether it predicts safeguards and crisis patterns.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. Residue policy may be a specialized rule-theory application.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:59:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://bpb-ap-se2.wpmucdn.com/thinkspace.csu.edu.au/dist/c/3891/files/2020/10/Asad-Anthropology.pdf: overlap: Close for the claim that practice, discipline, authority, embodiment, institutions, and historical tradition shape religious subject formation, so doctrine alone cannot explain outcomes.; difference: Asad does not build a comparative safety rubric for self-negating contemplative paths.; novelty impact: Moderate to large reduction for the anti-doctrine-alone and practice-ecology claims.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:65:Unlike VCE, Britton's adverse-effects work, Engler, Pargament, Lindbeck, Asad, upaya pedagogy, and prior Lumenary ledgers, this idea says that self-negating contemplative paths can be coded along three independent axes, operational capacity, residue policy, and training ecology, and that the interaction among those axes will predict safeguards, warnings, verification methods, and crisis patterns better than any one axis alone.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:69:Candidate: Dogen-style practice-realization, inherited devotional practice, radical Other Power, and secular mindfulness adverse effects strain the model from different sides.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:79:- If: Traditions with similar operational demands but different residue policies should interpret the same phenomenological event differently and verify it differently. Then: Practices that train attention, disidentification, and stable witnessing should diverge in whether the remainder is framed as conventional process, witness, Self, grace, vow, or non-ownable event, and these labels should forecast verification and warning practices. Weakens if: Practitioner reports and manuals interpret similar events without residue-policy effects, or the interpretive difference has no impact on verification, repair, or safety guidance. Test surface: Cross-coding Advaita self-inquiry, Buddhist de-identification, Mahamudra or Dzogchen recognition, Shin entrusting, and Christian surrender materials.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:89:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with recognition, guru relation, and post-recognition conduct
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:120:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.53. The idea is useful and testable, but its main components are strongly anticipated by prior Lumenary ledgers, VCE and Cheetah House style adverse-effects research, Engler's functional ego warning, Pargament's agency and coping styles, Lindbeck's grammar model, Asad's discursive-tradition account, upaya capacity pedagogy, and primary-text evidence. The remaining contribution is a clearer three-factor interaction hypothesis and a split-source testing protocol.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.md:128:- Compare predictive power against VCE influencing factors, Cheetah House adverse-event categories, Engler's developmental warning, Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck grammar, Asad discursive tradition, upaya pedagogy, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:25:- Huangbo, On the Transmission of Mind, Blofeld translation hosted at https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a1-chun-chou-record.htm and https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a2-chun-chou-record-cont.htm, read with Dogen Bendowa excerpts at https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and Soto shusho itto note at https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:27:Structural observation: SN 22.59 and SN 22.95 explicitly authorize seeing, observing, examining, disenchantment, release, and the knowledge that the task is done. That is a staged investigative grammar. Huangbo repeatedly treats seeking Mind with mind, forming concepts of the Way, or making the Way into a road as the very distortion. Dogen's practice-realization unity blocks a simple cause-then-result reading, while Soto material also says Dogen emphasized active practice because realization is already present. The candidate's gate is textually plausible, but only if it codes the native practice grammar rather than broad tradition names.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:29:Secondary literature gap: Search further in Collingwood on the logic of question and answer, Gadamer on the priority of the question, Asad on discursive tradition, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Austin on felicity conditions, Sharf and Katz on contextualism, Dogen scholarship on shusho itto, Chan studies on Huangbo and Bankei, Dzogchen direct-introduction literature, VCE and Cheetah House safety literature, and spiritual bypassing research.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:31:Risk of overread: High. The model can make search-refusal too clean. Huangbo taught through dialogue, Dogen built a practice institution, and Dzogchen no-path language often requires teacher transmission. The modern cohort is clear but narrow: stable over-managers and perfectionistic practitioners who audit their inner state. It is not for beginners needing inquiry, people using non-inquiry to avoid repair, OCD or scrupulosity, dissociation, severe depression, mania, psychosis, acute trauma, addiction withdrawal, or medical blackout concerns.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:37:- Huangbo Transmission of Mind no seeking using mind to seek Mind
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:38:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization one shusho itto practice verification
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:39:- Dzogchen no path no practice direct introduction teacher support
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:40:- spiritual bypassing self-monitoring meditation detachment empirical research
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:45:- Huangbo, On the Transmission of Mind, https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a1-chun-chou-record.htm and https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a2-chun-chou-record-cont.htm: overlap: Huangbo already says seeking, conceptual road-making, and using mind to seek Mind are errors.; difference: The candidate turns Huangbo's instruction into a comparative coding gate for residue analysis and a modern practice-safety rule.; novelty impact: Strong downgrade for the core insight that the search itself can be the problem.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:46:- Dogen Bendowa and Soto shusho itto, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: Practice and realization are treated as inseparable, which already blocks a simple before-and-after result model.; difference: The candidate groups Dogen with search-refusal paths, but Dogen still insists on active, continuous practice.; novelty impact: Moderate downgrade and anomaly pressure. Dogen supports the gate but resists any no-practice simplification.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:53:Unlike Huangbo, Dogen, Collingwood, Gadamer, VCE, and prior Lumenary no-management records, this idea's specific contribution is a precondition test before remainder coding: only ask what remains if the path first authorizes a self-negation event with an after.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:57:Candidate: Rinzai koan and huatou practice deliberately uses an impossible or destabilizing question to create great doubt, while Dzogchen can deny path and result yet still require direct introduction, teacher relation, and integration.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:65:- If: The precondition gate has independent coding value. Then: Blind coders using only doctrinal or instruction passages can sort cases into search-sequence, search-refusal, question-as-medicine, no-distance-with-support, and undecidable above chance before seeing warnings or repairs. Weakens if: Coders cannot agree, or their labels are just tradition labels, teacher style, or genre labels in disguise. Test surface: Inter-rater coding on SN 22.59, SN 22.95, Huangbo, Bendowa, Tannisho, one Dzogchen direct-introduction source, and one Rinzai koan source.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:73:- Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:74:- Chan or Zen teachers familiar with Huangbo and Bankei
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:76:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:108:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.46 to 0.36. The core no-seeking and no-result logic is old in Huangbo, Dogen, Dzogchen, Shinran-adjacent no-calculation sources, and prior Lumenary no-management records. Retain as an extended precondition-gate hypothesis only if split-source coding shows predictive gain.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.md:115:- Add Rinzai koan practice and Dzogchen direct introduction as anomaly classes, not supporting examples.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-a-clock-measures-a-path-8cd5d80af738d5d8.md:32:Risk of overread: Moderate to high. Proper time is a precise physical concept, while a life path is a metaphor. The model may confuse social comparison with real coordination duties, and Dogen may reject the self-path language because it separates a person from being-time.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-a-clock-measures-a-path-8cd5d80af738d5d8.md:51:- Dogen, Uji source card, notes/source-cards/buddhism-dogen-uji.md: overlap: Dogen's being-time already resists external time and treats each being or moment as time, not as a thing located inside time.; difference: The candidate speaks of my path or another path, which Dogen may treat as a reifying translation.; novelty impact: Anomaly and partial near-neighbor. It supports local answerability but strains path-self language.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-a-clock-measures-a-path-8cd5d80af738d5d8.md:58:Unlike Einstein, Minkowski, local becoming, Rovelli, Page-Wootters, Dogen, social clock theory, chrononormativity, and the prior Lumenary clock record, this idea's possible contribution is a testable practical distinction: separate owed coordination times from borrowed comparison times, then see whether that reduces behind-in-life distress without weakening punctuality or responsibility.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-a-clock-measures-a-path-8cd5d80af738d5d8.md:78:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen Uji
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:27:- Dogen, Bendowa, Kazuaki Tanahashi translation, https://www.lionsroar.com/just-wholeheartedly-sit/
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:31:Secondary literature gap: Search reached Pargament on religious problem-solving styles, Lindbeck on doctrine as rule or grammar, Dogen practice-realization sources, Longchen Rabjam Trekcho, Chinul sudden awakening and gradual cultivation, Srivaishnava prapatti debates, Gita action-doership passages, Shinran Other Power, and upaya literature. It did not fully close-read Lindbeck's full book, Pargament's full 1988 article, Tibetan commentarial material on direct introduction, Sanskrit Advaita sources on praptasya prapti, or Srivaishnava primary polemics. This blocks candidate-discovery status.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:37:- Pargament religion problem-solving process three styles self-directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:38:- George Lindbeck doctrine as grammar rules cultural linguistic model religion
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:40:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization one practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:46:- spiritual bypassing nondual premature realization claims
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:50:- George Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine, rule or grammar theory summarized in https://repository.up.ac.za/bitstream/handle/2263/64227/Kim_Study_2018.pdf: overlap: Very close for the idea that doctrine functions as communally authoritative rules for discourse, attitude, and action rather than only propositions or symbols.; difference: The candidate narrows grammar to practice appropriation and asks whether the grammar authorizes, dissolves, or denies claim-making.; novelty impact: Large reduction. The grammar-level move is known; the candidate's remaining contribution is an operational sub-rubric for practice functions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:51:- Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for distributing agency between human actor and God through self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles.; difference: The candidate adds traditions that refuse the agency frame itself and separates claimability stance from credit distribution.; novelty impact: Moderate to large reduction for regulatory traditions. Less reduction for dissolutive and ontological cases.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:53:- Dogen, Bendowa, Tanahashi translation, https://www.lionsroar.com/just-wholeheartedly-sit/: overlap: Very close for practice-realization identity and resistance to treating realization as a later object possessed by a practitioner.; difference: The candidate codes this as dissolutive claimability and predicts formalism or attainment-reification failure modes.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. The Dogen structure is known; the failure-mode prediction needs testing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:54:- Longchen Rabjam, Instruction on Trekcho, https://www.lotsawahouse.org/tibetan-masters/longchen-rabjam/lama-yangtik-trekcho-instruction: overlap: Close for primordial, self-arisen awareness and nonfabrication, while still giving concrete instructions, vows, devotion, and conduct safeguards.; difference: The candidate treats Dzogchen as ontological denial of produced acquisition, but Longchenpa also preserves regulatory practice pressures.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction and strong anomaly pressure, because one text can mix stance values without a clean stage shift.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:63:Unlike Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Pargament's religious agency styles, Nagarjuna's agent-action critique, Dogen's practice-realization, Dzogchen primordial purity, Advaita praptasya prapti, Srivaishnava effort-grace debates, upaya pedagogy, and prior Lumenary credit-distribution records, this idea says the first coding question is whether the claiming framework itself is authorized, dissolved, ontologically denied, or stage-dependent. Its possible contribution is not the anti-appropriation insight, but the rule that support-locus and forbidden-claimant rubrics are valid only after that prior stance is coded.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:77:- If: Ontological denial produces a distinctive premature-realization failure mode. Then: Advaita and Dzogchen teachers should report recurring cases where students use already-present language to avoid preparation, conduct, integration, or verification. Weakens if: These cases are no more common than in regulatory traditions, or spiritual bypassing explains them without reference to ontological claimability. Test surface: Practitioner interviews, adverse-practice reports, and comparison with spiritual-bypassing literature.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:83:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen's practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:85:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:91:- Contemplative clinicians familiar with spiritual bypassing and adverse meditation effects
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:100:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners say this is ordinary doctrine-as-grammar, religious coping, upaya, grace-effort theology, nondual pedagogy, spiritual bypassing, or prior Lumenary ledger language. Dissolutive and ontological teachers reject the rubric as reifying. Teachers cannot produce stance-specific repairs beyond familiar cautions against pride, laziness, premature claims, or poor integration.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:120:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.68 to about 0.60. The idea is not a discovery of anti-appropriation, non-doership, practice-realization, already-attained realization, grace-effort distribution, or stage-dependent cultivation. Those are well anticipated by primary texts, Lindbeck, Pargament, upaya pedagogy, and prior Lumenary records. The remaining contribution is a novel synthesis: claimability stance as a prior validity check for support-locus and forbidden-claimant coding.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:129:- Compare predictive power against Lindbeck grammar, Pargament agency styles, upaya pedagogy, grace-effort theology, spiritual bypassing literature, prior Capacity Ledger, Forbidden Claimant, Credit Distribution, Handoff Point, and Entry-Claimant Grammar.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-claimability-and-support-rubric-baeaa976a10337e6.md:130:- Use Longchenpa Trekcho, Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, Pure Land Other Power, Srivaishnava prapatti, and successful cross-training as anomaly tests rather than confirming examples.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Inherited practice and Dogen-style practice-realization cases, especially cradle religious formation and Soto Zen's refusal to separate practice from realization.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:31:      "test_surface": "Split-source manual coding across Shinran Pure Land, Theravada path-factor texts, Orange or Augustinian grace texts, Dogen practice-realization, and Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:32:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Coders cannot separate entry mechanism from claimant rule, or later safeguards can be predicted equally well from generic tradition labels, conversion-stage theory, religious socialization, or Pargament agency styles."
