reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:125:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners say this is just homeomorphic equivalence plus spiritual bypassing, pastoral discernment, and ordinary comparative caution, and that the worksheet changes no concrete guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:141:      "clinicians familiar with spiritual bypassing and contemplative adverse effects",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:150:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model risks forcing traditions into modern therapeutic repair language. Pure Land nembutsu, Dzogchen pointing-out, sacramental speech, Dogen practice-realization, communal prayer, and ritual duty may function through vow, grace, recognition, participation, or formation rather than a named wound. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: stable unsupported seekers facing meaning loss, digital comparison, loneliness, and achievement-contingent certainty. It is not fit for acute crisis, dissociation, psychosis, mania, severe depression, OCD or scrupulosity loops, addiction withdrawal, unsafe authority, or medical blackout concerns.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:151:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Before public use, read Panikkar on homeomorphic equivalence, Freiberger on comparative method, Jonathan Z. Smith on comparison as redescription, Wittgenstein on language games, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Asad on discursive tradition, Austin on speech acts, Pargament on religious coping, spiritual bypassing literature, and Lindahl and Palitsky on contemplative difficulties and worldview context.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:164:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Wittgenstein, Asad, spiritual bypassing, and VCE context research, this candidate says a borrowed spiritual sentence must be downgraded from convergence to new teaching whenever the repair target changes. That is a useful Lumenary gate, but most of its parts are established prior art."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:26:- Dogen Genjokoan practice-realization, https://brightwayzen.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/For-BWZ-Chant-Book-Genjokoan.pdf; Tannisho sections 6 and 8, Taitetsu Unno translation, https://nembutsu.cc/buddhism/the-tannisho/tannisho-sections-i-to-x/
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:28:Structural observation: MN 22 is a direct near-neighbor for proper use followed by release, but it also requires right grasp before release. The Heart Sutra denies attainment while retaining reliance and mantra, so undermining a result does not imply abandoning the method. Dogen strains the whole stage-completion frame because practice and realization are not cleanly separable. Tannisho strains practitioner-owned authority because nembutsu is presented as free of self-power and not a good act or practice from the practitioner's side. Together, the primary texts support a scoped coding heuristic, not a discovery-level doctrine.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:30:Secondary literature gap: The audit found strong near-neighbors in Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Sells on apophatic unsaying, Pargament agency and coping styles, spiritual materialism, spiritual bypassing, VCE and Cheetah House adverse meditation support, and multiple prior Lumenary audits. Full source reliability still requires reading upaya scholarship, Zen post-kensho training, Shinran scholarship, spiritual direction ethics, and practitioner manuals in original languages where possible.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:41:- Pargament religious problem solving styles self-directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:51:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, 1988, indexed in Religious Coping, https://link.springer.com/rwe/10.1007/978-3-030-24348-7_578: overlap: Already sorts religious agency by who carries problem-solving responsibility: self, God, or collaboration.; difference: It is about coping and agency with God, not post-threshold method authority or contemplative verification.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction for custody and support-locus language.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:56:Unlike MN 22, Smith, Sells, Pargament, spiritual-materialism warnings, VCE safety work, and prior Lumenary return or custody audits, this idea says that the specific interaction between boundary operation and post-threshold custody should predict when a helpful method becomes guidance, conduct, external accountability, rest, or a private judge of worth. That is a useful synthesis, but the structure is mostly inherited from recent internal records.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:60:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization, Tannisho Other Power, inherited religion with no discrete threshold, and valid daily repetition without a separable product.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:62:Why it strains the model: These cases refuse the assumed sequence of tool, result, and post-result authority. In Dogen, practice is not merely a ladder to be evaluated afterward. In Tannisho, efficacy is not owned by the practitioner or method. In inherited religion, the authority may be communal and continuous before any explicit insight. In faithful daily repetition, keeping the same form may be obedience or formation rather than self-surveillance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:76:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Apophatic predication refusal, Zen or Huangbo search-refusal, Dogen practice-realization, and radical Other Power in Shinran.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "These cases may not follow the sequence credit distribution constrains residue authorization. Apophatic silence can be driven by claims about language and divine transcendence. Huangbo-style search refusal blocks the operation that would generate residue. Dogen collapses practice and realization. Shinran relocates efficacy so thoroughly that nembutsu is framed as non-practice for the practitioner. If these are central cases, the model needs at least a third variable: search grammar, predication theory, or practice-realization structure."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:28:      "expected_observation": "Within one credit type, independently coded texts should show more than one residue policy. For example, ground-centered sources should separate Advaita positive authorization, Dzogchen self-resolving remainder, and apophatic undecidable silence.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:36:      "test_surface": "Compare interaction model against Pargament agency styles, VCE factors, Lutz matrix variables, and prior Lumenary ledgers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:37:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Warnings are better predicted by institution, teacher style, lineage politics, trauma risk, retreat intensity, or generic spiritual bypassing than by the credit-residue interaction."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:42:      "test_surface": "Micro-phenomenological interviews with Advaita, Theravada, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Zen, Pure Land, and Christian apophatic practitioners.",
