reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:93:      "source": "Pargament religious problem-solving styles, accessible summary at https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC1630686/ and related overview https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:129:      "source": "Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:150:    "Compare predictive power against Pargament agency styles, self-power and other-power, grace-effort theology, Katz contextualism, Lutz matrix, VCE influencing factors, apophatic unsaying, Madhyamaka non-positioning, and prior Lumenary ledgers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:155:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.72 to about 0.38. The exact two-variable partial-coupling structure is already present in prior Lumenary work, especially Practice Architecture as Upstream Condition for Remainder Phenomenology and the post-negation authorization convergence. External prior art strongly anticipates the components: Pargament for agency allocation, self-power and other-power scholarship for credit grammar, apophatic and Madhyamaka sources for non-positioning and silence, VCE and Lutz for multidimensional contemplative coding, and Katz for tradition-shaped experience. The surviving value is a bounded translation-strain coding protocol, not an original doctrine candidate.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:158:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners say the model is familiar agency, grace, no-self, apophatic, upaya, lineage, or nondual pedagogy language. They cannot name a repair or prediction that differs from ordinary teacher discernment, Pargament, VCE, or prior Lumenary ledgers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:169:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction and self-liberation",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:174:      "Psychologists of religion familiar with Pargament",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:185:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model can make credit distribution look upstream by definition. Apophatic silence may arise from a theory of predication rather than appropriation risk. Dzogchen and Zen may block the search sequence before residue appears. Pure Land may reject the whole self-owned capacity frame. If the same passages are used to code credit and residue, the model becomes circular.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:186:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit used accessible primary translations, local prior Lumenary audits and dialogues, open academic records, and practitioner-facing sources. It did not fully read Pargament's original 1988 article, Sells's full monograph, Katz's original essay, Longchenpa in Tibetan, Shankara in Sanskrit, or practitioner interviews. This prevents any uniqueness claim.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Rinzai koan and huatou great doubt, plus Advaita self-inquiry and Dzogchen or Mahamudra direct-recognition settings.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:30:      "test_surface": "Preregistered survey and interview study across Advaita self-inquiry, Theravada not-self analysis, Dzogchen or Mahamudra direct recognition, Zen koan practice, and secular mindfulness users.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:57:    "\"Varieties of Contemplative Experience\" practitioner factors interpretation meditation challenges",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:59:    "\"spiritual bypassing\" John Welwood unresolved issues spiritual practice",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:93:      "source": "John Welwood and spiritual bypassing literature"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:99:      "source": "Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE 2017, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:118:    "Add anomaly categories for Rinzai or huatou great doubt, Advaita self-inquiry, Dzogchen or Mahamudra direct recognition, clear-light sleep, cessation or nirodha, valid solitude, and persistent depersonalization or derealization.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:122:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.42 to 0.34. The dependent-variable attack is useful, but MN 2, spiritual materialism, spiritual bypassing, VCE, perfectionism research, and recent Lumenary records already cover much of the structure. Retain as an extended test protocol, not a doctrine discovery.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:125:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Originality falls if practitioners identify this as standard spiritual materialism, spiritual bypassing, MN 2 question caution, VCE differential diagnosis, or ordinary perfectionism care, and if they do not change screening or repair decisions after seeing the model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:138:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:150:    "risk_of_overread": "High. This may be MN 2, spiritual materialism, spiritual bypassing, VCE practitioner-factor analysis, perfectionism research, and prior Lumenary records in sharper language. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: stable high performers, founders, professionals, app meditators, and solo self-inquiry readers whose worth depends on producing a result. It is not for OCD or scrupulosity loops, persistent depersonalization or derealization, psychosis, mania, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, trauma activation, acute crisis, or people who need rest, support, accountability, or clinical care rather than another self-check.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:151:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Before publication, read VCE and Progress or Pathology by Lindahl and colleagues; Chogyam Trungpa on spiritual materialism; John Welwood and clinical literature on spiritual bypassing; Katz, Sharf, and Taves on experience and interpretation; self-focused attention, rumination, intolerance of uncertainty, need for closure, perfectionism, achievement-contingent self-worth, depersonalization and derealization sources; and Rinzai or huatou literature on deliberately cultivated great doubt.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-pressure-after-letting-go-may-be-yours-c940a054cf45d9ae.json:164:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike MN 2, spiritual materialism, spiritual bypassing, VCE, perfectionism research, and prior Lumenary question-fit records, this idea's separable claim is a dependent-variable test: post-negation remainder pressure should be predicted more by pre-practice achievement-contingency, control-seeking, intolerance of uncertainty, and need for closure than by tradition label once method, teacher, and context are controlled."
observations/codex/2026-05-30-stop-making-silence-judge-you.md:25:- Meditation-safety grounding: Lindahl et al., Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE 2017, separates experiences from interpretations, causes, remedies, teacher relationships, and social context, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:27:- Dogen, Genjokoan, Shohaku Okumura translation, https://brightwayzen.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/For-BWZ-Chant-Book-Genjokoan.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:30:Structural observation: The primary texts partly support the model but mostly lower novelty. MN 22 already gives a boundary operation in which the Dhamma is valid for crossing and then not to be grasped, so method validation and method release are staged together. The Heart Sutra negates attainment but preserves reliance on Prajnaparamita, which is almost an exact prior structure for boundary cancellation plus retained custody. Tannisho relocates efficacy to Amida's Original Vow, denies self-powered merit, rejects teacher ownership, and restricts reading to those mature in faith, so custody, verification, and warning are already internally linked. Dogen strains the whole threshold premise: practice-enlightenment and verification by all things collapse the gap between method and completion, making boundary and custody look less like two variables and more like an analyst's grid imposed on a no-threshold practice field.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:32:Secondary literature gap: The audit used accessible primary translations, local Lumenary audits and dialogues, open academic records, and practitioner-facing sources. It did not read Japanese, Sanskrit, Pali, Tibetan, Greek, Arabic, or Latin originals, and it did not interview teachers. Further work should read Asad, Lindbeck, Weber, Sharf, Hori, Sells, Pargament, VCE research, Dogen scholarship, Pure Land scholarship, and apophatic theology in greater depth before any stronger novelty claim.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:34:Risk of overread: High. The model can become circular if boundary, custody, verification, and reentry are inferred from the same passage. It can also translate salvation, liberation, grace, lineage, conduct, and ritual into a modern governance vocabulary of attention and authority. Some traditions may refuse the threshold frame, especially Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, radical Other Power, apophatic predication refusal, and traditions where authorization is political, communal, sacramental, or continuous rather than contemplative.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:39:- Talal Asad discursive tradition authorized practice correct form purpose religion authority
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:42:- George Lindbeck doctrine as grammar cultural linguistic rule theory
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:43:- Varieties of Contemplative Experience influencing factors teacher community practice worldview
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:44:- Pargament religion problem-solving self-directing deferring collaborative coping agency God practitioner
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:45:- Dogen practice realization verification Genjokoan Bendowa
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:53:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://voidnetwork.gr/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Idea-of-an-Anthropology-of-Islam-by-Talal-Asad.pdf: overlap: Close structural prior. Asad's discursive tradition foregrounds authorized instruction about correct practice, tradition, power, and the regulation of proper performance.; difference: Asad is not specifically modeling contemplative threshold operations or custody of freed attention.; novelty impact: High reduction for the authority-first and native-practice-first move.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:54:- George Lindbeck, doctrine as grammar and cultural-linguistic rule theory, overview at https://www.saet.ac.uk/Christianity/TheologicalLanguage: overlap: Close. Lindbeck already treats doctrine as a grammar that shapes religious speech, perception, action, and communal rules.; difference: The candidate operationalizes a narrower threshold codebook for boundary, custody, verification, and reentry.; novelty impact: Moderate to high reduction. The model may be a specialized comparative workflow for doctrine-as-grammar.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:57:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, accessible summary, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for agency and custody distribution across human and divine roles: self-directing, deferring, and collaborative patterns already formalize different responsibility allocations.; difference: Pargament studies coping and God-related agency, not contemplative boundary operations after self-weakening practice.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. Custody rules need baseline comparison against established religious agency models.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:58:- Lindahl et al., The Varieties of Contemplative Experience, PLOS ONE, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239: overlap: Close methodological prior. VCE separates phenomenology, interpretation, teacher and community factors, practice factors, remedies, impairment, and integration.; difference: VCE does not isolate boundary operation plus custody rule as an interaction predicting verification and reentry.; novelty impact: High methodological reduction. The candidate must outperform VCE-style multidimensional coding.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:64:Unlike Asad, Lindbeck, Sharf, Hori, Pargament, VCE research, MN 22, the Heart Sutra, and prior Lumenary authority and custody ledgers, this idea's surviving distinct claim is a narrow interaction protocol: code boundary operation and custody rule independently, then test whether their interaction predicts held-out verification, teaching permission, warning, repair, and reentry patterns better than doctrine, tradition label, stage, institution, boundary alone, or custody alone. Without that split-source predictive gain, it is mostly a consolidation of prior work.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:68:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization identity, radical Other Power in Tannisho, inherited communal religion, and apophatic refusal in Dionysius.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:70:Why it strains the model: Dogen removes the gap between method and result, so there may be no threshold where boundary and custody can be assigned. Tannisho places decisive working in Amida's vow while warning against self-calculation, so calling entrusting a local custody handoff can reintroduce the self-power frame the text resists. Inherited religion may mature by continuity and ritual participation rather than by a discernible handoff. Dionysius places the divine Cause beyond affirmation and negation, which destabilizes God as a simple custody recipient.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:76:- If: Boundary operation and custody rule interact rather than merely adding two descriptive labels. Then: Split-source coders who code boundary operation from one corpus and custody rule from another should predict held-out verification signs, teaching permission, warning profiles, and reentry disciplines above tradition-label, doctrine-only, boundary-only, and custody-only baselines. Weakens if: The interaction term adds no predictive power, or the same predictions are explained by institution type, teacher style, stage sequence, social ecology, or clinical-risk variables. Test surface: Pre-registered coding of Advaita, Theravada, Rinzai, Soto, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Jodo Shinshu, Christian apophatic practice, and Sufi fana or baqa sources.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:85:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:89:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction and stabilization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:93:- Psychologists of religion familiar with Pargament's agency and coping work
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:121:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.42. The exact language is fresh, but both axes and much of the predictive burden are already present in prior Lumenary records: Method's Reckoning, Custody of Unclaimed Attention, Authority-Boundary Ecology, Custody and Receiving Surface, and related entry and support ledgers. External prior art also strongly anticipates the components: Asad and Lindbeck for native authority and grammar, Sharf and Katz-style contextualism for suspicion of experience-first comparison, Hori for Zen training and verification, Pargament for agency distribution, VCE for multidimensional contemplative difficulty coding, MN 22 for validated-then-released method, Heart Sutra for no-attainment plus reliance, Tannisho for Other Power custody, and Dogen for practice-realization anomaly. The surviving value is a bounded split-source interaction test, not a doctrine candidate or strong original discovery.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:130:- Compare predictive value against Asad discursive tradition, Lindbeck grammar, Weberian authority, Sharf and Katz contextualism, Pargament agency styles, upaya pedagogy, VCE variables, institution type, teacher style, social ecology, clinical risk, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:132:- Close-read MN 22, Heart Sutra, Dogen Genjokoan or Bendowa, Tannisho, Cloud of Unknowing, Dionysius Mystical Theology, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out source, and one Sufi fana or baqa source before further scoring.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:25:- Dogen Bendowa practice-realization sources, for example https://everydayzen.org/teachings/dogens-bendowa-part-2-of-3/, read against Shinran and Jodo Shinshu Other Power sources, for example https://www.nembutsu.info/standard/nature_faith.htm
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:28:Structural observation: Dogen strains the boundary model because practice and realization are not cleanly separable, so a category such as continuous practice-realization must not be treated as just another boundary type. Shinran strains the same model from another side: efficacy is relocated to Amida's vow and Other Power, not to a practitioner-owned method or generic support system. These two cases may both refuse self-owned attainment, but their warnings differ: Dogen pressure falls on expecting realization outside practice, while Shinshu pressure falls on self-power calculation. Lachs then shows that Zen authorization language and transmission mechanisms can legitimate hierarchy and authority while creating problems in Western Zen. The safety sources add a further split: religious authority, community trust, and doctrinal legitimacy can coexist with coercion, silence, institutional betrayal, or inadequate survivor response.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Before promotion, read Asad on discursive tradition, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Weber on religious authority, Bell on ritualization, Sharf and Katz on experience and context, Freiberger and J. Z. Smith on comparison, Popper and Mayo on test structure, Lachs on Zen authorization, Ann Gleig and Amy Langenberg on Buddhist misconduct and survivor-centered method, IICSA and FaithTrust safeguarding materials, AIFS on spiritual and religious abuse, VCE and Cheetah House on meditation-related difficulties, plus actual ethics codes from Soto Zen, Insight, Vajrayana, Christian spiritual direction, and interfaith settings.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:37:- Talal Asad discursive tradition authority correct practice tradition pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:38:- George Lindbeck doctrine as grammar religious practice authority
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:43:- Varieties of Contemplative Experience teacher community support adverse effects meditation Lindahl Britton
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:52:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://voidnetwork.gr/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Idea-of-an-Anthropology-of-Islam-by-Talal-Asad.pdf; George Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine; Max Weber, sociology of religious authority.: overlap: Close structural prior for authority as historically transmitted practice, discipline, grammar, legitimacy, and power, rather than private experience or generic doctrine.; difference: These sources do not provide the candidate's exact split-source test with match grain, held-out prediction, and separate seeker safety axis.; novelty impact: Strongly reduces originality of the authority-ecology component.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:57:- Lindahl, Fisher, Cooper, Rosen, and Britton, Varieties of Contemplative Experience, https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0176239; Cheetah House, https://www.cheetahhouse.org/ and https://www.cheetahhouse.org/faq.: overlap: Close methodological prior for coding practice factors, teacher and community relationships, adverse effects, interpretation, remedies, clinical exclusions, and support needs.; difference: VCE and Cheetah House do not code native legitimacy or comparative convergence, but they already require safety variables that the candidate must not replace.; novelty impact: Moderate to strong downgrade for practice-testability and safety design.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:62:Unlike Asad, Lindbeck, Weber, Freiberger, Smith, Popper, Lachs, Gleig and Langenberg, VCE, Cheetah House, safeguarding literature, and the parent Lumenary records, the only separable contribution is a combined protocol: code native authority ecology from one source layer, pre-register match grain and held-out predictions before any positive convergence verdict, then report native legitimacy and safety adequacy as separate outputs for human use. The broader ideas are not new.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:74:- If: Native authority ecology plus grained match conditions are predictive variables, not just descriptive vocabulary. Then: Coders who see only source passages on authorization, practice-realization, Other Power, conduct evidence, and teaching permission can predict held-out warnings, safeguards, repair instructions, and re-entry obligations above tradition-label and institution baselines. Weakens if: Held-out predictions are no better than broad tradition identity, teacher style, institutional policy, or generic Asad-Lindbeck authority coding. Test surface: Split-source blind coding across Soto Zen, Rinzai Zen, Jodo Shinshu, Theravada, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Christian spiritual direction, Sufism, and secular mindfulness.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-grained-authority-ecology-safety-audit-10826d16d65c0fa0.md:75:- If: The match-grain rule prevents cheap positive convergence. Then: Pairs such as Dogen practice-realization and Shinran Other Power can share only a narrowly stated structure, such as refusal of self-owned attainment, while still predicting different warnings and permissions. Confirmed matches should be rare, specific, and tied to held-out observations. Weakens if: Coders confirm broad categories such as relocated efficacy across many pairs without predicting distinct warnings, or cannot agree on match grain before outcome evidence. Test surface: Inter-rater trial requiring coders to write match grain and prediction before seeing manuals, ethics rules, or practitioner interviews.
